ortant%20points%20you%E2%80%99re%20making%20both%20about%20the%20Israeli%20people%20and%20about%20the%20Israeli%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDI%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20It%E2%80%99s%20exactly%20how%20you%20framed%20it%3B%20it%E2%80%99s%20exactly%20how%20you%20framed%20it.%20Israel%20is%20democratic%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20its%20tailored%20democracy%2C%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20serving%20the%20interest%20of%20the%20Jewish%20citizens%20of%20Israel%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20seeing%20other%20people%20as%20human%20beings%2C%20it%20fails.%20When%20it%20comes%20to%20treating%20its%20own%20citizens%20as%20equal%20citizens.%20it%20fails.%20When%20it%20comes%20to%20addressing%20what%20its%20own%20state%20has%20been%20practising%20against%20another%20nation%20%E2%80%93%20you%20know%2C%20we%20are%20witnessing%20a%20second%20%3Cem%3ENakba%3C%2Fem%3E%3A%20forced%20eviction%20orders%2C%20you%20know%2C%20forces%20displacements%2C%20collective%20punishments%2C%20genocide.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUnfortunately%2C%20what%20the%20Jewish%20people%20had%20suffered%20in%20the%20Holocaust%20is%20being%20repeated%20by%20themselves%20on%20the%20Palestinians%20today.%20This%20is%20the%20sad%20reality%20that%20we%20should%20be%20learning%20from%20history%2C%20we%20should%20be%2C%20you%20know%2C%20safeguarding%20and%20protecting%20humanity.%20We%20should%20be%2C%20you%20know%2C%20prevailing%20justice%20and%20humanity%20over%20all%20those%20violence%20and%20crimes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUnfortunately%2C%20the%20Israeli%20public%20is%20not%20saying%20what%20should%20be%20said%20to%20their%20own%20leadership.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKT%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20That%E2%80%99s%20a%20very%20important%20point%20you%20made%20which%20I%E2%80%99ll%20repeat%20for%20the%20audience%20before%20I%20go%20to%20my%20next%20question.%20What%20the%20Jews%20suffered%20during%20the%20Holocaust%20is%20exactly%20what%20Israel%20is%20doing%20today%20to%20the%20Palestinians%20and%20that%20is%20not%20just%20a%20paradox%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20an%20irony%20that%20the%20Jews%20are%20doing%20to%20others%20what%20happened%20to%20them%20without%20realising%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMy%20last%20question%20about%20the%20Palestinians%20who%20are%20citizens%20of%20Israel%2C%20before%20I%20come%20to%20other%20categories%20of%20Palestinians%3A%20what%20sort%20of%20political%20involvement%20beyond%20voting%20is%20permitted%20to%20the%20Palestinian%20citizens%20of%20Israel%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EWatch%20%7C%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Watch%20%7C%20Gaza%20Crisis%20to%20Last%20Months%2C%20Get%20Lot%20Worse%20Before%20it%20Calms%3A%20Former%20Palestine%20Minister%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Fwatch-gaza-israel-crisis-karan-thapar-ghassan-khatib%5C%22%3EGaza%20Crisis%20to%20Last%20Months%2C%20Get%20Lot%20Worse%20Before%20it%20Calms%3A%20Former%20Palestine%20Minister%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDI%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Well%2C%20you%20know%2C%20the%20situation%20for%20the%20Palestinian%20citizens%20of%20Israel%20is%20really%20dire%20and%20it%E2%80%99s%20really%E2%80%A6%20the%20framing%20is%20second%20or%20third-class%20citizens.%20They%20can%20vote%2C%20they%20can%20run%20for%20elections%3B%20however%2C%20it%20has%20been%20documented%20that%20the%20Israeli%20authorities%20made%20sure%20to%20maintain%20and%20to%20accelerate%20the%20levels%20of%20crimes%20between%20the%20Palestinian%20communities%20inside%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20levels%20of%20drugs%2C%20for%20example%E2%80%A6%20so%20they%20are%20trying%20to%20convert%20and%20to%20transform%20the%20Palestinian%20communities%20into%20really%2C%20a%20bad%20image%20of%20communities%20which%20don%E2%80%99t%20deserve%20equal%20rights.%20Unfortunately%2C%20this%20has%20been%20happening%20systematically%20against%20the%20Palestinian%20communities%20inside%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Palestinians%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20are%20mostly%20educated%20and%20most%20of%20them%20go%20into%20medicine%20and%20nursing%20and%20really%20the%20most%20scientific%20fields.%20So%20they%20are%20still%20needed%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20hospitals%20and%20medical%20service%2C%20yet%20they%20are%20not%20enjoying%20political%20rights%20as%20equal%20citizens%20of%20Israel%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20the%20Jewish%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBefore%20we%20finish%2C%20I%20also%20want%20to%20mention%20the%20settler%20terror%20because%20we%20were%20speaking%20about%20the%20Holocaust%20comparison.%20Last%20January%20and%20February%2C%20we%20have%20witnessed%20the%20settler%20terror%20all%20over%20the%20West%20Bank%2C%20in%20Huwara%E2%80%A6%20It%20was%20called%20by%20the%20Israelis%20themselves%20%5Bas%20a%5D%20pogrom%2C%20it%20was%20really%20a%20repetitive%20scenario%20of%20what%20the%20Israeli%20Jewish%20people%20have%20suffered%20under%20the%20Holocaust.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKT%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Absolutely%2C%20now%20that%20we%E2%80%99ve%20begun%20talking%20about%20Israeli%20settlers%2C%20let%E2%80%99s%20come%20to%20the%20Palestinians%20who%20live%20in%20the%20West%20Bank%2C%20where%20many%20view%20Israel%20as%20a%20colonising%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThese%20people%2C%20these%20Palestinians%20in%20the%20West%20Bank%2C%20are%20not%20citizens%20of%20Israel.%20So%20first%2C%20let%20me%20start%2C%20what%20sort%20of%20rights%20do%20they%20have%20under%20Israeli%20occupation%20and%20control%20of%20the%20West%20Bank%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDI%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Palestinians%2C%20you%20mean%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKT%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20That%E2%80%99s%20right.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26171625%2FAreas-A-B-C.png%5C