occupation%20had%20been%20entrenched%20under%20the%20cover%20of%20a%20peace%20process%2C%20under%20the%20cover%20of%20the%20sugar-coated%20negotiations.%20On%20the%20ground%2C%20for%20the%20past%2030%20years%2C%20the%20number%20of%20settlers%20have%20more%20than%20tripled.%20Today%20we%20have%20more%20than%20750%2C000%20settlers%20living%20in%20settlements%2C%20you%20know%2C%20dividing%20the%20West%20Bank.%20There%20is%20no%20territorial%20contiguity%20between%20any%20Palestinian%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESo%20when%20they%20advocate%20for%20the%20two-state%20solution%2C%20geopolitically%20speaking%2C%20and%20you%20know%2C%20on%20the%20ground%2C%20it%20is%20not%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EYou%20know%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20a%20professor%20of%20diplomacy%20and%20I%20am%20a%20very%20big%20fan%20of%20bringing%20about%20the%20two-state%20solution%20for%20a%20strategic%20solution%20for%20the%20Palestinian%20and%20the%20Israeli%20people%20alike.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20if%20we%20are%20realistic%20and%20if%20we%20take%20a%20realpolitik%20approach%20on%20the%20ground%2C%20the%20Israeli%20settlements%20are%20basically%2C%20you%20know%2C%20the%20reason%20behind%20putting%20the%20Palestinians%20in%20small%20ghettos%2C%20divided%20and%20surrounded%20by%20those%20settlements%20which%20basically%20hinder%20any%20possibility%20of%20any%20two-state%20solution.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKT%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Absolutely%2C%20for%20an%20Indian%20audience%20I%20just%20clarify%20that%20the%20West%20Bank%20is%20supposed%20to%20be%20%E2%80%93%20under%20the%201967%20agreements%20%E2%80%93%20a%20Palestinian%20state%2C%20but%20because%20Israeli%20settlers%2C%20750%2C000%2C%20have%20settled%20in%20the%20West%20Bank%20creating%20little%20pockets%20and%20islands%2C%20it%20is%20impossible%20now%20for%20the%20West%20Bank%20to%20actually%20ever%20take%20the%20shape%20of%20a%20separate%20autonomous%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20has%20been%20a%20deliberate%20Israeli%20policy%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20West%20Bank%20can%20never%20become%20a%20Palestinian%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELet%20me%20then%20ask%20you%20what%20is%20the%20relationship%20between%20these%20750%2C000%20settlers%20and%20the%20Palestinian%20people.%20What%20sort%20of%20relationship%20do%20they%20have%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2Fbopc9EQOEps%3Fsi%3Dxlz8XWUI9Qx1b3Q4%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDI%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20They%20are%20weaponised%2C%20they%20are%20militarised%2C%20they%20practise%20terror%20on%20the%20Palestinians.%20They%20are%20treated%20as%20first-class%20citizens%20in%20comparison%20with%20the%20Palestinians.%20Unfortunately%2C%20the%20Palestinian%20citizens%20are%20suffering%20from%20the%20attacks%20and%20from%20the%20violence%20and%20terrorism%20that%20those%20settlers%20are%20practising%20against%20the%20Palestinian%20civilians%20and%20guess%20what%3F%20They%20are%20protected%20by%20the%20Israeli%20military%20army.%20Military%20soldiers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EI%20also%20want%20to%20clarify%20to%20the%20Indian%20audience%20that%20they%20need%20to%20understand%20that%2030%20years%20ago%2C%20the%20Palestinians%20had%20made%20a%20big%20concession%2C%20because%20we%20believe%20in%20peace%2C%20because%20we%20believe%20in%20the%20rights%20of%20the%20peoples%20of%20Israel%20to%20live%20in%20peace%20and%20security.%20We%20agreed%20to%20the%20two-state%20solution%20on%20the%20%E2%80%9867%20border%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20means%20that%20we%20gave%20up%20on%2078%25%20of%20historic%20Palestine.%20We%20accepted%20%E2%80%93%20as%20the%20PLO%2C%20which%20is%20the%20legitimate%20representative%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20people%20%E2%80%93%20we%20accepted%20to%20have%20our%20own%20state%20on%2022%25%20of%20Mandated%20Palestine.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20two-state%20solution%20was%20the%20position%20of%20the%20international%20community.%20It%20was%20the%20concession%20that%20the%20PLO%20gave%20in%20our%20will%20and%20hopes%20for%20bringing%20peace%2C%20prosperity%20and%20security%20to%20the%20Palestinians%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Israelis.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhat%20did%20we%20gain%20after%2030%20years%20of%20procrastinated%20so-called%20peace%20talks%3F%20More%20settlers%2C%20more%20settlements%2C%20no%20possibility%20on%20the%20ground%20of%20any%20independence%20of%20sovereignty%20for%20the%20Palestinian%20people.%20More%20extrajudicial%20killings%20on%20a%20daily%20basis%2C%20more%20detentions%20%E2%80%93%20you%20know%20that%205%2C200%20Palestinians%20are%20still%20%5Bbehind%5D%20Israeli%20bars%2C%20you%20know%2C%20inside%20the%20Israeli%20prisons%2C%20suffering%20from%20every%20kind%20of%20racism%20and%20punishment.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20are%201%2C264%20who%20are%20administratively%20detained%2C%20and%20I%20want%20to%2C%20you%20know%2C%20explain%20this%20to%20the%20Indian%20audience%20because%20I%E2%80%99m%20sure%20they%20haven%E2%80%99t%20heard%20about%20administrative%20detention%20before.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAdministrative%20detention%20only%20exists%20in%20Israel.%20This%20is%20a%20very%20illegal%20way%20of%20detaining%20and%20arresting%20people%2C%20where%20they%20can%20basically%20renew%20the%20arrest%20every%20six%20months%20without%20putting%20them%20to%20court%2C%20without%20putting%20them%20to%20trial%2C%20without%20giving%20them%20the%20chance%20to%20see%20a%20lawyer.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECan%20you%20imagine%2C%20you%20know%2C%20140%20of%20those%20are%20women%20and%20170%20of%20those%20are%20children.%20Where%20on%20Earth%20in%202023%20can%20you%20imagine%20that%20a%20state%2C%20a%20state%20that%20has%20the%20recognition%20of%20the%20world%20order%2C%20you%20know%2C%20abuses%20the%20rights%20of%20civilians%2C%20practises%20apartheid%2C%20practices%20every%20kind%20of%20racism%2C%20administrative%20detention%2C%20arrests%20on%20daily%20basis%2C%20confiscations%20of%20lands%20%5Band%5D%20extrajudicial%20killings%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fgaza-palestine-israel-health-benjamin-netanyahu%5C%22%3EGaza%E2%80%99s%20Health%20System%20Had%20Already%20Been%20Weakened%20%E2%88%92%20the%20Siege%20Pushed%20it%20into%20Crisis%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWe%20face%20on%20a%20daily%20basis%2C%20incursions%2C%20raids%2C%20killings%2C%20violence%2C%20settler%20terror.%20Everything%20is%20documented%20today%20and%20the%20world%20is%20an%20open%20world%20of%20communication.%20It%E2%80%99s%20sad%20that%20we%20are%20still%20telling%20our%20story%20under%20the%20Israeli%20occupation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20root%20cause%20of%20what%20we%20are%20witnessing%20for%20the%20Palestinians%20and%20the%20Israelis%20alike%2C%20if%20we%20are%20calling%20for%20peace%2C%20we%20need%20to%20start%20by%20ending%20the%20Israeli%20military%20occupation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKT%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Absolutely.%20And%20as%20you%20said%20%E2%80%93%20I%E2%80%99m%20just%2C%20again%2C%20highlighting%20this%20for%20an%20Indian%20audience%20%E2%80%93%20even%20your%20hope%20of%20being%20able%20to%20form%20an%20independent%2C%20sovereign%20Palestine%20state%20on%20just%2022%25%20has%20been%20quashed%20by%20the%20settlers%20and%20the%20fact%20that%20you%20can%E2%80%99t%20do%20so%20%5Bsic%5D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnd%20it%20also%20means%20that%20because%20of%20continuing%20Israeli%20control%20on%20what%20is%20accepted%20internationally%20as%20your%20land%2C%20you%E2%80%99re%20even%20there%20second-class%20citizens.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENow%20I%20notice%2C%20since%20October%207th%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20quoting%20%3Cem%3EAl%20Jazeera%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9Cover%2091%20Palestinian%20people%20in%20the%20West%20Bank%20have%20been%20killed%20in%20clashes%20with%20settlers.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20since%20the%207th%20of%20October.%20Are%20these%20clashes%20a%20recent%20development%20or%20have%20they%20been%20happening%20regularly%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDI%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Israelis%20tried%20to%20mislead%20audiences%20that%20this%20whole%20thing%20started%20on%20the%207th%20of%20October.%20Let%E2%80%99s%20truly%20explain%20the%20reality%20and%20convey%20the%20reality%20and%20the%20right%20narration%2C%20because%20people%20in%20India%20deserve%20to%20learn%20the%20truth%3A%20that%20Israel%20had%20been%20manipulating%2C%20had%20been%20executing%2C%20had%20been%20practising%20apartheid%20and%20occupation%20against%20the%20Palestinian%20people%20for%2075%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20crimes%2C%20under%20international%20law%2C%20under%20humanitarian%20international%20law%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20all%E2%80%A6%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20need%20to%20really%20interpret%20things%20or%20to%20be%20clever%20about%20it.%20Doesn%E2%80%99t%20really%20take%20a%20genius%20to%20discover%20that%20the%20Israeli%20military%20occupation%20had%20been%2C%20you%20know%2C%20targeting%20every%20Palestinian%2C%20have%20been%20extrajudicially%20killing%20the%20Palestinians%2C%20have%20been%20targeting%20our%20lands%2C%20confiscating%20them%20for%20the%20for%20the%20interest%20of%20building%20more%20settlements.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20settler%20colonial%20project%20has%20been%20ongoing%20for%20so%20long.%20The%20Israeli%20state%20is%20built%20on%20the%20doctrine%20of%20settler%20colonialism%20that%20we%20have%20been%20suffering%20from%20for%20a%20long%2C%20long%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fgaza-apartheid-israel-and-the-last-stand-of-settler-colonialism%5C%22%3EGaza%2C%20Apartheid%20Israel%20and%20the%20Last%20Stand%20of%20Settler%20Colonialism%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20message%20that%20the%20world%20needs%20to%20hear%20is%20that%20those%20states%20who%20have%20recognised%20the%20state%20of%20Israel%20for%2075%20years%20today%20need%20to%20realise%20that%20Israel%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20have%20a%20border%20line%20until%20today.%20Why%3F%20Why%20don%E2%80%99t%20we%20start%20by%20asking%20Israel%20to%20define%20its%20borderline%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20they%20say%20they%20want%20peace%2C%20when%20they%20say%20%E2%80%A6%20that%20the%20Palestinians%20deserve%20peace%2C%20I%20want%20to%20tell%20the%20Indian%20people%20that%20no%20Israeli%20leader%20has%20ever%20uttered%20the%20word%20%E2%80%98state%20for%20the%20Palestinians%E2%80%99%20or%20the%20%E2%80%98right%20of%20self-determination%20for%20the%20Palestinian%20people%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20contrary%2C%20they%20have%20been%20ongoing%20with%20their%20settler%20colonial%20project%2C%20with%20their%20terrorism%20against%20the%20Palestinians%2C%20more%20killings%2C%20more%20detentions%2C%20and%20more%20treating%20us%20as%20minorities%20who%20are%20only%20entitled%20to%20very%20minimal%20religious%20rights%2C%20in%20the%20case%20that%20we%20are%20not%20even%20allowed%20to%20go%20to%20Bethlehem%20or%20Jerusalem%20to%20even%20pray.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhat%20the%20Israelis%20have%20been%20trying%20is%20to%20mislead%20audiences%20and%20unfortunately%20the%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.wiktionary.org%2Fwiki%2Fhasbara%5C%22%3Ehasbara%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20Israeli%20propaganda%2C%20the%20investments%20they%20put%20in%20their%20narratives%20had%20to%20a%20certain%20extent%20succeeded%20in%20misleading%20audiences%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKT%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Now%20the%20third%20category%20of%20Palestinian%20people%20are%20in%20Gaza.%20They%20live%20under%20a%20Hamas%20government%2C%20but%20they%E2%80%99re%20blockaded%20and%20besieged%20on%20three%20sides%20by%20Israel%20and%20on%20one%20by%20Egypt.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhat%20sort%20of%20authority%20and%20control%20has%20Israel%20exercised%20over%20their%20lives%20since%202005%20when