20a%20ground%20invasion.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20actually%20what%20you%E2%80%99re%20saying%20is%20life%20for%20people%20in%20Gaza%20has%20been%20pretty%20miserable%20for%2016-17%20years%3B%20even%20though%20the%20Israelis%20claim%20they%20have%20withdrawn%2C%20they%E2%80%99ve%20encircled%20it%20and%20blockaded%20it%2C%20they%20prevented%20things%20coming%20in%20%5Band%5D%20going%20out%2C%20and%20the%20Gazans%20have%20been%20suffering%20for%20a%20very%20long%20time%20%E2%80%93%20that%E2%80%99s%20the%20point%20you%E2%80%99re%20making%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDI%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Yes%2C%20for%20the%20past%2015%20years%2C%20the%20Gaza%20people%2C%202.2%20million%20civilians%2C%20suffered%20four%20wars%2C%20four%20incursions%3Cem%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Efour%20attacks%20on%20the%20civilians%20of%20Gaza.%20Those%20people%20%E2%80%93%20and%20this%20is%20the%20fifth%20war%2C%20which%20started%20on%20October%207%20%E2%80%93%20the%20people%20in%20Gaza%20were%20totally%20deprived%20from%20the%20basic%20minimum%20human%20rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EYou%20should%20know%20that%20people%20in%20Gaza%20don%E2%80%99t%20even%20enjoy%20the%20services%20of%202G%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20the%20internet.%20You%20know%2C%20this%20is%20a%20human%20need%20in%20the%2021st%20century%3B%20let%20alone%20electricity%2C%20let%20alone%20water%2C%20let%20alone%20mobility%20rights%2C%20education%20rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPeople%2C%20two%20million%20civilians%2C%20were%20left%20with%20no%20hope%2C%20no%20reason%20to%20live.%20They%20really%20suffocated%20the%20people%20%E2%80%93%20thousands%2C%20thousands%20of%20young%2C%20smart%2C%20intelligent%20youth%20chose%20to%20go%20in%20the%20sea%2C%20seek%20refuge%20and%20you%20know%20prefer%20to%20die%20in%20the%20sea%20rather%20than%20to%20live%20under%20the%20Israeli%20military%20blockade%2C%20inside%20a%20big%20open%20air%20prison%20of%20365%20kilometres%2C%20deprived%20from%20the%20basic%20human%20needs%20in%20the%2021st%20century.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKT%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20You%E2%80%99ve%20said%20something%20that%20will%20shake%20people%3A%20people%20in%20Gaza%20don%E2%80%99t%20even%20have%202G.%20And%20I%E2%80%99m%20told%20people%20in%20Gaza%20for%20years%2C%20if%20not%20decades%2C%20have%20been%20used%20to%20six%20and%20eight-hour%20power%20cuts%20regularly.%20They%E2%80%99ve%20been%20used%20to%20shortage%20of%20water%20regularly.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThat%20has%20been%20the%20condition%20in%20which%20they%E2%80%99ve%20lived%20long%2C%20long%20before%20October%207.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fhindutva-israel-tweets-palestine-conflict%5C%22%3EUnpacking%20the%20Hindutva%20Embrace%20of%20Israel%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDI%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Yes.%20Yes%2C%20and%20this%20is%20what%20people%20need%20to%20realise.%20Those%20people%20were%20%5Bput%20in%5D%20a%20pressure%20cooker.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EYou%20deprive%20them%20from%E2%80%A6%20can%20you%20imagine%20living%20without%20the%20internet%20for%20one%20hour%20today%3F%20Here%20I%20am%20addressing%20young%20people%20and%20old%20people%2C%20and%20everybody%2C%20you%20know%2C%20we%20cannot%20live%20without%20smartphones%2C%20without%20communicating%20with%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECan%20you%20imagine%20that%20in%202023%2C%20for%2016%20years%2C%20people%20are%20hearing%20about%20us%20communicating%2C%20about%E2%80%A6%20and%20here%20we%20need%20to%20maybe%20clarify%20that%20people%20in%20the%20West%20Bank%20also%20enjoy%20only%203G%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnd%20this%20is%20all%20under%20an%20Israeli%20decision%20of%20depriving%20the%20Palestinians%20of%20this%20minimal%20human%20need.%20This%20is%20not%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20okay%20to%20tolerate%20that%20Israel%20is%20practising%20all%20those%20kinds%20of%20racism%2C%20crimes%20against%20humanity%2C%20against%20the%20Palestinians%2C%20and%20the%20people%20are%20watching%20and%20are%20ke