%20Egypt.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMy%20question%20is%20a%20little%20different%3A%20Given%20the%20life%20Palestinians%20are%20forced%20to%20live%20in%20Israel%20or%20in%20the%20West%20Bank%20or%20in%20Gaza%2C%20would%20the%20Palestinian%20people%20themselves%20welcome%20the%20prospect%20of%20going%20to%20Jordan%20and%20Egypt%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDI%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Palestinian%20people%20have%20suffered%20from%20the%20%3Cem%3ENakba%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%201948%20and%20then%20the%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FNaksa_Day%5C%22%3ENaksa%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%201967%2C%20so%20I%20think%20we%20have%20learned%20the%20lesson%20very%2C%20very%20well.%20And%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20Palestinian%20refugees%20are%20still%20deprived%20of%20their%20basic%20right%20of%20return%2C%20I%20think%20the%20population%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20people%20will%20not%20leave%20and%20will%20not%20accept%20the%20forced%20displacement%20orders.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it%20is%20time%20that%20audiences%20realise%20that%20Israel%20has%20been%20systematically%20colonising%20and%20this%20settler%20colonial%20project%20has%20been%20ongoing.%20This%20%5Bwar%20of%20late%5D%20is%20being%20framed%20as%20an%20Israel-Hamas%20war%20because%20this%20is%20a%20logical%20argument%20that%20they%20could%20convince%20audiences%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20reality%20they%20are%20using%20this%20pretext%2C%20they%20are%20using%20Hamas%20as%20a%20fig%20leaf%2C%20but%20their%20target%20is%20Gaza%2C%20is%20the%20land%2C%20is%20to%20evict%20the%20Palestinian%20people%2C%20is%20to%20continue%20to%20annex%20the%20land%20as%20part%20of%20their%20settler%20colonial%20project%20which%20will%20continue%20also%20in%20the%20West%20Bank.%20They%20are%20hoping%20that%20the%20Palestinian%20people%20will%20be%20evicted.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThat%E2%80%99s%20why%20the%20Jordanian%20and%20the%20Egyptian%20position%2C%20which%20might%20sound%20a%20little%20bit%20inhumane%20in%20face%20of%20the%20sufferings%20of%20the%20millions%20of%20civilians%2C%20but%20on%20the%20political%20level%20we%20need%20to%20realise%20that%20they%20are%20saving%20the%20Palestinian%20national%20project%2C%20which%20is%20part%20of%20the%20deal%20of%20the%20century.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThat%E2%80%99s%20why%20we%20see%20the%20USA%2C%20the%20shuttle%20diplomacy%20from%20Blinken%20and%20Biden%20providing%20this%20legal%20coverage%20for%20the%20Israeli%20war%20crimes%20against%20the%20Palestinian%20people%2C%20it%20is%20basically%20to%20serve%20their%20interests%20in%20their%20electoral%20campaigns%20coming%20soon%2C%20and%20for%20the%20right-wing%20leaders%2C%20of%20course%2C%20in%20Europe%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20also%2C%20because%20this%20is%20a%20pragmatic%20scenario%20of%20a%20win-win%2C%20a%20cake%20sharing%20scenario%20for%20the%20Israel%2C%20the%20US%20and%20many%20other%20regional%20players%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20national%20rights%2C%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20right%20to%20self-determination%2C%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20the%20lives%20of%20two%20million%20civilians%20living%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fisrael-palestine-conflict-india-forsakerole-voice-of-moderation%5C%22%3EIsrael-Palestine%20Conflict%3A%20Why%20Has%20India%20Forsaken%20Its%20Role%20as%20a%20Voice%20of%20Moderation%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKT%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Permit%20me%20one%20last%20question%20before%20I%20let%20you%20go.%20I%20know%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20this%20interview%20you%20said%20you%20passionately%20support%20the%20concept%20of%20a%20two-state%20solution.%20But%20is%20it%20still%20feasible%20and%20practical%20with%20750%2C000%20Jewish%20settlers%20in%20the%20West%20Bank%20and%20with%20Israel%20having%20declared%20the%20whole%20of%20Jerusalem%20as%20its%20capital%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIs%20a%20two-state%20solution%20still%20possible%20or%20would%20you%20agree%20with%20someone%20like%20Gideon%20Levy%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EHaaretz%3C%2Fem%3E%20correspondent%2C%20who%20said%20to%20me%20in%20an%20interview%20on%20Saturday%20that%20a%20one-state%20solution%20with%20equal%20rights%20for%20Jews%20and%20Arabs%2C%20with%20equal%20rights%20for%20Israelis%20and%20Palestinians%2C%20is%20the%20most%20sensible%20solution%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnd%20he%20said%20Israelis%20may%20not%20accept%20it%20today%20because%20it%E2%80%99s%20emotionally%20difficult.%20Palestinians%20may%20not%20accept%20it%20because%20it%E2%80%99s%20emotionally%20difficult%2C%20but%20that%20has%20to%20be%20the%20solution.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWould%20you%20agree%20with%20him%20or%20would%20you%20say%20no%2C%20this%20is%20too%20idealistic%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDI%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20No%2C%20he%E2%80%99s%20very%20realistic%2C%20because%20if%20you%20live%20here%2C%20if%20you%20commute%20north%20to%20south%20here%2C%20you%20will%20see%2C%20realistically%20and%20logically%20speaking%2C%20if%20you%20take%20the%20reasoning%20of%20reality%2C%20it%20is%20not%20possible%20anymore%20to%20have%20a%20Palestinian%20state%2C%20given%20all%20the%20settlements%2C%20the%20divisions%2C%20and%20given%20all%20the%20military%20system%2C%20that%20is%20the%20occupation%20system%2C%20that%20is%20entrenched%2C%20that%20is%20hindering%20any%20possibility%20for%20the%20Palestinian%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELet%20alone%20Netanyahu%20and%20his%20leaders%20and%20his%20government%E2%80%99s%20statements%20of%20saying%20no%20to%20Palestinian%20state.%20The%20fact%20that%20they%20are%20saying%20no%20to%20a%20Palestinian%20state%2C%20no%20to%20peace%20talks%2C%20no%20to%20negotiations%2C%20make%20us%20have%20%E2%80%93%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20wishful%20scenario%20of%20having%20a%20one-state%20reality.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhy%20would%20I%20say%20no%20to%20a%20one%20state%20reality%2C%20if%20I%20want%20to%20honour%20civilians%2C%20if%20I%20want%20to%20honour%20humanity%2C%20if%20I%20want%20to%20end%20the%20sufferings%20of%20the%20millions%20of%20Palestinian%20people%20under%20the%20Israeli%20military%20occupation%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20under%20equal%20rights%2C%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20an%20apartheid%20state.%20The%20fact%20that%20Israel%20is%20trying%20to%20export%20what%20is%20happening%20here%20as%20a%20religious%20issue%20has%20led%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20Israelis%20will%20not%20accept%20a%20one-state%20%5Bsolution%5D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBecause%20this%20is%20not%20a%20Jewish-Muslim%20or%20a%20Jewish-Muslim-Christian%20conflict.%20No%2C%20it%20is%20a%20conflict%20over%20land.%20It%20is%20a%20settler%20colonial%20project.%20We%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20a%20problem%20with%20the%20Jews.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EYou%20know%2C%20I%20have%20many%20Jewish%20friends%20all%20around%20the%20world%2C%20I%20studied%20with%20many%20of%20them%2C%20I%20have%20colleagues%2C%20many%20of%20them%2C%20and%20I%20keep%20good%2C%20positive%20and%20healthy%20relationships%20with%20many%20of%20them.%20Those%20who%20are%20enlightened%2C%20those%20who%20are%20in%20education%2C%20those%20who%20believe%20in%20me%20as%20an%20equal%20citizen.%20This%20is%20the%20message%20that%20we%20need%20to%20realise.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIf%20Dalal%20Iriqat%20in%20Palestine%2C%20and%20Shlomo%20in%20Tel%20Aviv%20or%20Herzliya%2C%20or%20Ahmed%20in%20Pakistan%20or%20in%20India%20or%20in%20New%20York%20or%20in%20Paris%20or%20in%20Shanghai%20or%20in%20Greenland%2C%20are%20seen%20as%20equal%20human%20beings%2C%20then%20we%20will%20not%20look%20at%20the%20shape%20of%20the%20solution%20but%20we%20will%20look%20for%20humanity%20and%20for%20justice%20for%20every%20civilian%20%E2%80%93%20whether%20it%20is%20Muslim%2C%20Christian%2C%20Jewish%2C%20Buddhist%20or%20atheist.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20message%20that%20we%20need%20to%20hear%20%E2%80%93%20the%20Palestinians%20are%20not%20being%20treated%20or%20viewed%20by%20the%2