ast%20few%20years%26quot%3B%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report.%20The%2075-year-old%20former%20Australia%20captain%2C%20who%20also%20had%20a%20controversial%20stint%20as%20the%20head%20coach%20of%20the%20Indian%20team%20from%202005-2007%2C%20admitted%20that%20he%20is%20doing%20fine%20but%20is%20certainly%20not%20living%20a%20life%20of%20luxury%20as%20a%20result%20of%20his%20cricketing%20career.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20on%20the%20bones%20of%20my%20a**e%2C%26quot%3B%20Chappell%20told%20News%20Corp.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20certainly%20don't%20want%20it%20to%20sound%20like%20we're%20in%20desperate%20straits%2C%20because%20we're%20not%20-%20but%20we're%20not%20living%20in%20luxury%20either.%20I%20think%20most%20people%20assume%20that%2C%20because%20we%20played%20cricket%2C%20that%20we%20are%20all%20living%20in%20the%20lap%20of%20luxury.%20While%20I'm%20certainly%20not%20crying%20poor%2C%20we're%20not%20reaping%20in%20the%20benefits%20that%20today's%20players%20are%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20report%2C%20Chappell%20%26quot%3Breluctantly%26quot%3B%20agreed%20to%20a%20GoFundMe%20page%20being%20set%20up%20for%20him%2C%20along%20with%20a%20testimonial%20lunch%20held%20at%20the%20Melbourne%20Cricket%20Ground%20(MCG)%20last%20week%20-%20hosted%20by%20Eddie%20McGuire%20and%20attended%20by%20cricket%20greats%2C%20including%20brothers%20Ian%20and%20Trevor.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EChappell%20further%20said%20he%20is%20not%20the%20only%20player%20from%20his%20era%20who%20experienced%20financial%20difficulties%2C%20even%20though%20the%20landscape%20of%20professional%20cricket%20has%20come%20a%20long%20way%20since%20his%20retirement.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20just%20my%20friends%20who%20realised%20that%20we%20didn't%20get%20a%20lot%20and%20just%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20Judy%20and%20I%20were%20comfortable%20in%20our%20retirement%2C%26quot%3B%20Chappell%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20be%20fair%2C%20there%20are%20others%20of%20our%20era%20who%20are%20in%20more%20dire%20circumstances%20that%20could%20do%20with%20the%20help%20and%20I%20don't%20think%20the%20game%20has%20done%20enough%20for%20players%20of%20that%20era.%20Particularly%20in%20relation%20to%20the%20comparison%20with%20today's%20era.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BI%20believe%20the%20players%20that%20set%20the%20scene%20for%20what's%20happening%20today%2C%20should%20probably%20be%20recognised%20for%20the%20role%20they%20played%20in%20getting%20the%20game%20to%20where%20it%20is%20today%2C%26quot%3B%20Chappell%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPacer%20Dennis%20Lillee%2C%20wicketkeeper%20Rod%20Marsh%2C%20and%20Chappell%20were%20part%20of%20an%20iconic%20trio%20that%20defected%20to%20Kerry%20Packer's%20World%20Series%20Cricket%20in%20the%20late%201970s.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20unlike%20Lillee%20and%20Marsh%2C%20Chappell%20didn't%20receive%20a%20fundraising%20testimonial%20at%20the%20end%20of%20his%20career%20to%20help%20set%20him%20up%20after%20retiring%20from%20cricket.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20report%20in%20news.com.au%20quotes%20Chappell's%20friends%20saying%20that%20he%20is%20doing%20it%20tougher%20than%20an%20Australian%20sporting%20legend%20ever%20should.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGreg%20is%20a%20very%20proud%20man.%20He's%20doing%20it%20tougher%20than%20what%20he%20says%2C%26quot%3B%20Chappell's%20friend%20Peter%20Maloney%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Australian%20great%20also%20runs%20the%20Chappell%20Foundation%2C%20which%20raises%20funds%20for%20homelessness%20charities.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20foundation%20makes%20sure%20every%20cent%20is%20distributed%20each%20year%20and%20Chappell%20doesn't%20keep%20any%20money%20for%20himself.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Chappell%20Foundation%20is%20run%20by%20Darshak%20Mehta%20and%20100%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20money%20that%20is%20raised%20gets%20distributed%2C%26quot%3B%20Maloney%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20distribute%20it%20annually%20so%20at%20the%20end%20of%20each%20year%2C%20they%20don't%20leave%20any%20money%20and%20they're%20starting%20afresh.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20put%20your%20name%20to%20a%20foundation%20you're%20entitled%20to%20take%20some%20money%20out%20of%20it.%20But%20Greg%20hasn't%20taken%20a%20cent%20out%20of%20it%2C%20even%20though%20he%20could%20have.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20guess%20that%20was%20the%20irony%20that%20he%20was%20the%20face%20of%20it%20and%20turning%20up%20to%20every%20function%20and%20he's%20raising%20all%20this%20money%20while%20he%20didn't%20have%20a%20hell%20of%20a%20lot%20himself.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPut%20it%20this%20way%2C%20we%20will%20probably%20end%20up%20raising%20about%20%24250%2C000%20out%20of%20it%2C%20and%20it%20will%20significantly%20enhance%20his%20last%20few%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20Maloney%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EChappell%20has%20had%20a%20forgettable%20tenure%20with%20the%20Indian%20cricket%20team.%20The%20then%20coach%20Chappell%20didn't%20share%20a%20cordial%20relation%20with%20legendary%20Indian%20players%20like%20Sachin%20Tendulkar%20and%20Sourav%20Ganguly%20during%20his%20stint.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGreg's%20tenure%20as%20coach%20was%20the%20worst%20of%20my%20career.%20There%20is%20no%20doubt%20we%20failed%20as%20a%20collective%20in%202007%2C%20but%20his%20high-handed%20manner%20added%20to%20our%20disappointment%20and%2C%20in%20the%20immediate%20aftermath%20of%20defeat%2C%20had%20a%20harmful%20impact%20on%20Indian%20cricket%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Tendulkar%20as%20quoted%20by%20Hindustan%20Times.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EChappell%20scored%2024%20centuries%20across%2087%20Tests%20during%20the%201970s%20and%2080s%20and%20led%20Australia%2048%20times.%20He%20retired%20from%20Tests%20in%20January%201984%20as%20the%20highest%20run-getter%20(7110)%20in%20Australian%20Test%20history%2C%20surpassing%20Sir%20Donald%20Bradman's%20record%20of%206996%20runs.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E(With%20PTI%20Inputs)%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698321360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2F4t7aqc48_rahul-dravid-greg-chappell-afp_625x300_26_October_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fcontroversial-ex-indian-cricket-team-coach-greg-chappell-facing-financial-struggle-friends-raise-funds-4515888%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Cricket%20legend%20Greg%20Chappell%20has%20revealed%20going%20through%20a%20financial%20struggle%20with%20his%20friends%20pitching%20in%20to%20set%20up%20an%20online%20fundraising%20platform%20to%20%26quot%3Benhance%20his%20last%20few%20years%26quot%3B%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fcontroversial-ex-indian-cricket-team-coach-greg-chappell-facing-financial-struggle-friends-raise-funds-4515888%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fcontroversial-ex-indian-cricket-team-coach-greg-chappell-facing-financial-struggle-friends-raise-funds-4515888%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fcontroversial-ex-indian-cricket-team-coach-greg-chappell-facing-financial-struggle-friends-raise-funds-4515888%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tamil%20Nadu%20Governor's%20Big%20Charge%20Day%20After%20Petrol%20Bomb%20Thrown%20At%20Home%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Raj%20Bhavan%20on%20Thursday%20said%20police%20did%20not%20register%20its%20complaint%20on%20the%20petrol%20bomb%20issue%2C%20and%20alleged%20a%20fair%20probe%20was%20%26quot%3Bkilled%26quot%3B%20before%20it%20began%2C%20setting%20off%20the%20latest%20flashpoint%20between%20the%20ruling%20DMK%20and%20the%20Governor.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20further%20alleged%20that%20the%20police%20diluted%20the%20%26quot%3Battack%26quot%3B%20as%20an%20act%20of%20simple%20vandalism%20and%20did%20not%20take%20up%20detailed%20interrogation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20man%20was%20arrested%20for%20throwing%20a%20petrol%20bomb%20at%20a%20gate%20of%20the%20Raj%20Bhavan%20in%20Chennai.%20The%20man%20had%20tried%20to%20do%20the%20same%20thing%20outside%20a%20BJP%20office%20in%20the%20city%20a%20few%20months%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPolice%20did%20not%20register%20Raj%20Bhavan%20complaint%20on%20attack.%20Suo%20moto%20diluted%20the%20attack%20as%20act%20of%20simple%20vandalism%20and%20in%20a%20hurry%20got%20arrested%20the%20accused%20and%20remanded%20(him)%20to%20jail%20at%20midnight%20waking%20up%20the%20magistrate%20and%20prevented%20detailed%20interrogation%20which%20could%20expose%20those%20behind%20attack%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Raj%20Bhavan%20posted%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFair%20investigation%20is%20killed%20before%20it%20began%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20police%2C%20however%2C%20say%20an%20FIR%20was%20registered%20based%20on%20the%20complaint%20by%20a%20police%20personnel%20present%20on%20the%20spot.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThey%20say%20the%20Raj%20Bhavan's%20complaint%20was%20received%20only%20around%2011%20pm%20and%20that%20the%20details%20mentioned%20in%20it%20too%20would%20be%20taken%20up%20during%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERuling%20DMK's%20Law%20Minister%20S%20Regupathy%2C%20condemning%20the%20incident%2C%20underlined%20that%20there%20was%20no%20security%20lapse.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Raj%20Bhavan%20is%20well%20protected.%20Investigation%20is%20underway%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Minister%20said%20denying%20there%20was%20any%20security%20lapse.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EVinod%2C%20the%20man%20who%20has%20been%20arrested%2C%20was%20in%20jail%20for%20eight%20months%20for%20throwing%20petrol%20bomb%20outside%20the%20BJP%20office%20in%20Chennai%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Minister%20expressed%20suspicion%20if%20the%20man%20suspected%20to%20be%20suffering%20from%20mental%20health%20issues%20%26quot%3Bwas%20staged%20to%20do%20this%20to%20tarnish%20the%20state%20government's%20image%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20Raj%20Bhavan's%20allegations%20of%20filthy%20abuses%20by%20DMK%20leaders%20and%20allies%20on%20the%20Governor%2C%20Mr%20Regupathy%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20only%20responded%20to%20Governor's%20allegations%20for%20people%20to%20understand.%20We%20never%20spread%20hatred%20against%20him.%20It's%20the%20Governor%20who%20spreads%20hatred%20across%20Tamil%20Nadu%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20the%20Raj%20Bhavan%20said%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Battacked%26quot%3B%2C%20and%20that%20%26quot%3Bmiscreants%20carrying%20bombs%20tried%20to%20barge%20in%20through%20the%20main%20gate%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20police%20complaint%20it%20targeted%20the%20DMK%20for%20what%20it%20calls%20%26quot%3Bvicious%20attacks%20on%20the%20Governor%20using%20filthy%20abuses%20and%20wielding%20threats%20to%20his%20life....by%20leaders%20and%20workers%20of%20DMK%20and%20allies%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BThese%20threats%20are%20intended%20to%20overawe%20the%20Governor%20and%20restrain%20his%20constitutional%20duties%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECiting%20past%20police%20complaints%2C%20the%20Raj%20Bhavan%20said%20%26quot%3Bcomplaints%20lodged%20with%20the%20police%20have%20been%20inconsequential%20due%20to%20police%20inaction%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGovernor%20R%20N%20Ravi%20has%20had%20a%20series%20of%20tussles%20with%20the%20ruling%20party%20from%20delaying%20assent%20for%20bills%20passed%20in%20the%20assembly%20to%20pushing%20Sanatan%20Dharma%20in%20his%20speeches%2C%20something%20perceived%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20as%20an%20ideology%20that%20promotes%20caste%20discrimination%20and%20oppression.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERN%20Ravi%20had%20also%20avoided%20reading%20names%20of%20leaders%20including%20Ambedkar%2C%20Annadurai%20and%20M%20Karunanidhi%20in%20his%20official%20assembly%20speech%20and%20walked%20out%20when%20the%20house%20moved%20a%20resolution%20to%20not%20record%20