20ways%20to%20treat%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20was%20Sherika%20De%20Armas%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20model%20represented%20Uruguay%20at%20the%20international%20level%20in%202015.%20At%20the%20competition%20in%20Sanya%2C%20China%2C%20she%20couldn't%20make%20it%20to%20the%20top%2030%2C%20but%20she%20was%20only%20among%20six%2018-year-olds%20at%20that%20time%20of%20competition.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20was%20complimented%20for%20her%20%26quot%3Bbeautiful%20face%2C%20towering%20height%20and%20charismatic%20personality%26quot%3B%2C%20with%20one%20outlet%20calling%20Ms%20De%20Armas%20%26quot%3Bone%20of%20the%20young%20promising%20talents%20of%20Uruguay.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20always%20wanted%20to%20be%20a%20model%2C%20whether%20a%20beauty%20model%2C%20an%20advertising%20model%20or%20a%20catwalk%20model%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20had%20told%20NetUruguay%20after%20the%202015%20competition.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20dangerous%20is%20cervical%20cancer%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20World%20Health%20Organisation%20(WHO)%2C%20cervical%20cancer%20is%20the%20fourth%20most%20common%20cancer%20in%20women.%20The%20Clinical%20Oncology%20Society%20said%20that%20an%20estimated%20341%2C831%20women%20died%20from%20cervical%20cancer%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20cervical%20cancer%20usually%20spreads%20in%20four%20ways%3A%20From%20cervix%20to%20the%20uterus%2C%20outside%20the%20cervix%20or%20uterus%20but%20is%20detected%20before%20reaching%20the%20walls%20of%20the%20pelvis%2C%20reaching%20lower%20part%20of%20the%20vagina%2C%20and%20finally%20to%20the%20lining%20of%20the%20bladder%2C%20the%20rectum%2C%20or%20to%20distant%20organs%20and%20bones%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.healthline.com%2Fhealth%2Fcervical-cancer%2Fcan-you-die-from-cervical-cancer%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EHealthline%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EAbout%20the%20new%20treatment%3C%2Fst