Dubey%20was%20allowed%20to%20explain%20his%20allegations%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20the%20CBI%20complaint%2C%20Mr%20Dubey%20had%20written%20to%20Lok%20Sabha%20Speaker%20Om%20Birla%20and%20levelled%20cash-for-query%20allegations%20against%20Ms%20Moitra.%20The%20Trinamool%20MP%20has%20called%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20lawyer%20her%20%26quot%3Bjilted%20ex%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESome%20opposition%20members%20raised%20questions%20over%20Mr%20Dubey's%20intent%20because%20Ms%20Moitra%20had%20highlighted%20the%20issue%20of%20his%20educational%20qualifications.%20Mr%20Dubey%2C%20however%2C%20said%20he%20has%20already%20got%20a%20clean%20chit%20on%20this%20matter%2C%20sources%20said.%20v%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20letter%20claimed%20to%20share%20%26quot%3Birrefutable%20evidence%26quot%3B%20of%20businessman%20Darshan%20Hiranandani%20giving%20bribes%20to%20Ms%20Moitra%20to%20ask%20questions%20in%20parliament.%20The%20questions%20were%20allegedly%20designed%20to%20target%20the%20Adani%20Group.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20ethics%20committee%20will%20give%20a%20report%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20Speaker%20%26quot%3Bas%20early%20as%20possible%26quot%3B%2C%20people%20with%20direct%20knowledge%20of%20the%20matter%20told%20NDTV%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20Pawan%20Bansal%20committee%20that%20gave%20its%20report%20in%20just%20two%20weeks%20in%20December%202005%20in%20the%20infamous%20cash-for-questions%20scam%20when%20the%20United%20Progressive%20Alliance%20(UPA)%20was%20in%20power%20in%20the%20centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Dehadrai%20told%20reporters%20the%20proceedings%20were%20%26quot%3Bcordial%20and%20pleasant%26quot%3B%20and%20he%20answered%20all%20the%20questions%20the%20ethics%20committee%20asked.%20%26quot%3BEverything%20was%20very%20cordial%20and%20they%20were%20very%20pleasant.%20Some%20questions%20were%20put%20to%20me%20and%20I%20have%20answered%20those%20questions%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20while%20leaving.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Dubey%20said%20he%20will%20be%20available%20whenever%20the%20ethics%20committee%20calls%20him.%20%26quot%3BThey%20were%20normal%20questions...%20All%20I%20can%20say%20is%20the%20MPs%20are%20concerned.%20When%20they%20call%20me%20next%20I%20will%20come.%20The%20question%20is%20whether%20the%20propriety%20and%20dignity%20of%20parliament%20will%20hold.%20It%20is%20a%20question%20of%20the%20dignity%20of%20parliament.%20The%20ethics%20committee%20is%20more%20worried%20than%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Dubey%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20affidavit%2C%20Mr%20Hiranandani%20alleged%20the%20Trinamool%20MP%20shared%20her%20MP%20email%20so%20that%20he%20could%20send%20her%20information%20and%20she%20could%20raise%20the%20questions%20in%20parliament.%20He%20alleged%20she%20later%20gave%20him%20her%20parliament%20login%20and%20password%20for%20him%20to%20post%20the%20questions%20directly.%20The%20ethics%20committee%20reaching%20out%20to%20the%20Information%20Technology%20Ministry%20and%20the%20Home%20Ministry%20is%20linked%20to%20the%20alleged%20misuse%20of%20the%20parliament%20login%20ID%20and%20password%20by%20Ms%20Moitra.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMs%20Moitra%20has%20denied%20the%20allegations%20and%20said%20she%20is%20prepared%20for%20any%20inquiry.%20She%20has%20also%20said%20that%20she%20is%20ready%20to%20answer%20questions%20from%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20ethics%20committee.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENeither%20The%20Trinamool%20nor%20its%20INDIA%20bloc%20allies%20have%20come%20out%20in%20support%20of%20Ms%20Moitra%20so%20far.%20The%20Trinamool%20has%20said%20it%20will%20not%20comment%20on%20the%20case.%20The%20party's%20leader%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20Derek%20O'Brien%2C%20has%20said%20they%20will%20take%20an%20appropriate%20decision%20on%20the%20allegations%20against%20Ms%20Moitra%20after%20the%20parliamentary%20panel%20completes%20its%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698318480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-07%2Fvaflt8ic_mahua-moitra-p