20scrapping%20its%20iconic%20McFlurry%20spoon%20after%20nearly%2030%20years%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221168%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20in%20a%20car%20eats%20a%20McDonald's%20McFlurry%20with%20a%20spoon%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F653a41540487ff031caeec48%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMcDonald's%20is%20getting%20rid%20of%20its%20hollow%20plastic%20McFlurry%20spoons%20in%20the%20US.%3Cp%3EMcDonald's%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMcDonald's%20is%20ditching%20its%20hollow%20plastic%20McFlurry%20spoons%20in%20the%20US%2C%20it%20announced%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20current%20spoons%20serve%20a%20double%20purpose%20%E2%80%93%20they're%20used%20to%20stir%20toppings%20into%20the%20ice%20cream.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMcDonald's%20is%20replacing%20them%20with%20the%20smaller%20spoons%20used%20for%20sundaes%2C%20which%20it%20says%20use%20less%20plastic.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMcDonald's%20is%20scrapping%20its%20iconic%20hollow%20McFlurry%20spoons%20after%20nearly%20three%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20burger%20giant%20announced%20on%20Tuesday%20that%20US%20restaurants%20would%20be%20ditching%20the%20utensil%2C%20starting%20this%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20McDonald's%20spokesperson%20previously%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foodandwine.com%2Fnews%2Fmcdonalds-mcflurry-spoon-straw-free-deal%23%3A~%3Atext%3D%2522The%2520McFlurry%2520spoon%2520was%2520invented%2Cin%25201995%252C%2522%2520McDonald%2527s%2520explains.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFood%20%26amp%3B%20Wine%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20spoons%20that%20are%20now%20being%20phased%20out%20were%20first%20introduced%20back%20in%201995.%20The%20spoons%20have%20been%20an%20object%20of%20intrigue%20for%20years%2C%20with%20diners%20wondering%20why%20they're%20hollow%20and%20what%20the%20purpose%20of%20the%20hook%20on%20the%20top%20is.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20McDonald's%20has%20previously%20set%20the%20record%20straight%20on%20the%20unusual%20design%20of%20the%20spoons%3A%20They%20double%20as%20spindles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20make%20a%20McFlurry%2C%20McDonald's%20staff%20pour%20soft-serve%20ice%20cream%20into%20a%20cup%20and%20then%20sprinkle%20topping%20onto%20it.%20They%20then%20insert%20the%20hollow%20plastic%20spoon%2C%20which%20is%20attached%20to%20a%20McFlurry%20machine%20and%20used%20to%20mix%20toppings%20into%20the%20ice-cream.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20chain's%20US%20restaurants%20are%20now%20transitioning%20to%20reusable%20spindles%20that%20are%20swapped%20out%20and%20cleaned%20after%20each%20McFlurry%20is%20made.%20The%20desserts%20will%20then%20be%20served%20with%20a%20smaller%20black%20spoon%2C%20the%20same%20one%20that%20McDonald's%20already%20gives%20out%20with%20its%20sundaes%2C%20which%20it%20says%20%26quot%3Buses%20less%20plastic.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20small%20change%20will%20help%20reduce%20single-use%20plastic%20waste%20in%20restaurants%2C%26quot%3B%20McDonald's%20said%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcorporate.mcdonalds.com%2Fcorpmcd%2Four-stories%2Farticle%2Fmcflurry-spindles-intheus-aregetting-more-sustainable-makeover.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estatement%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20company%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mcdonalds.com%2Fgb%2Fen-gb%2Fnewsroom%2Farticle%2Fnew-paper-based-cutlery.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eannounced%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20October%20that%20it%20was%20switching%20to%20compostable%2C%20paper-based%20McFlurry%20spoons%20in%20the%20UK.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reddit.com%2Fr%2FMcDonaldsEmployees%2Fcomments%2F16ycj7l%2Fid_like_to_point_out_this_mcbullshit%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20a%20photo%20shared%20on%20a%20Reddit%20forum%20for%20McDonald's%20employees%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20new%20spoon%20given%20to%20customers%20buying%20a%20McFlurry%20will%20be%20individually%20wrapped.%20The%20photo%20also%20appears%20to%20show%20that%20the%20new%20reusable%20spindles%20are%20pink%2C%20with%20employees%20instructed%20to%20use%20the%20spindles%20for%20four%20hours%20before%20swapping%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcorporate.mcdonalds.com%2Fcorpmcd%2Four-purpose-and-impact%2Four-planet%2Fpackaging-toys-and-waste.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOther%20steps%3C%2Fa%3E%20McDonald's%20has%20been%20taking%20to%20cut%20back%20on%20plastic%20use%20include%20using%20paper-based%20straws%2C%20McFlurry%20cups%20without%20plastic%20lids%2C%20and%20introducing%20salad%20boxes%20and%20cutlery%20made%20from%20renewable%20fiber.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMcDonald's%20US%20menu%20features%20two%20core%20McFlurry%20flavors%3A%20Oreo%20and%20M%26amp%3BM.%20It%20also%20sells%20a%20range%20of%20time-limited%20flavors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInsider%20has%20contacted%20McDonald's%20for%20comment%20on%20whether%20this%20affects%20both%20corporate%20and%20franchise%20restaurants%2C%20whether%20the%20changes%20will%20be%20introduced%20outside%20the%20US.%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmcdonalds-removes-mcflurry-spoon-ice-cream-machine-dessert-spindle-mix-2023-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698317528000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F653a4180356802a56be46a11%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmcdonalds-removes-mcflurry-spoon-ice-cream-machine-dessert-spindle-mix-2023-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22McDonald's%20is%20replacing%20the%20hollow%20McFlurry%20spoons%20with%20the%20smaller%20spoons%20served%20with%20sundaes%2C%20which%20it%20says%20use%20less%20plastic.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22gdean%40insider.com%20(Grace%20Dean)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A13%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmcdonalds-removes-mcflurry-spoon-ice-cream-machine-dessert-spindle-mix-2023-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20Did%20Kotak%20Mahindra%20Bank%20Ignore%20Internal%20Talent%20and%20Choose%20a%20CEO%20With%20Negligible%20Indian%20Experience%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F21164943%2Fimage-1155.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20October%2021%2C%20Kotak%20Mahindra%20Bank%20(KMB)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kotak.com%2Fcontent%2Fdam%2FKotak%2Fabout-us%2Fmedia-press-releases%2F2023%2FCEO-Appointment-Final.pdf%5C%22%3Eannounced%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India%20(RBI)%20has%20approved%20the%20appointment%20of%20Ashok%20Vaswani%20as%20the%20bank%E2%80%99s%20next%20managing%20director%20and%20chief%20executive%20officer.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20been%20appointed%20as%20MD%20and%20CEO%20for%20a%20period%20of%20three%20years.%20He%20will%20join%20on%20January%201%2C%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EVaswani%E2%80%99s%20selection%20was%20unexpected%2C%20as%20the%20media%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Findia-business%2Fwhole-time-directors-seen-to-succeed-kotak-at-bank%2Farticleshow%2F103335821.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20shortlisting%20of%20two%20internal%20candidates%20for%20RBI%E2%80%99s%20approval.%20They%20were%20K.P.S.%20Manian%2C%20head%20of%20corporate%2C%20institutional%20and%20investment%20banking%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kotak.com%2Fcontent%2Fdam%2FKotak%2Fabout-us%2Fexecutive-board%2FKotak_Shanti_Ekambaram%2520_Profile.pdf%5C%22%3EShanti%20Ekambaram%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20head%20of%20consumer%20banking.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPrakash%20Apte%2C%20chairman%20of%20KMB%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kotak.com%2Fcontent%2Fdam%2FKotak%2Fabout-us%2Fmedia-press-releases%2F2023%2FCEO-Appointment-Final.pdf%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20pleased%20to%20announce%20that%20%5Bthe%5D%20RBI%20has%20approved%20the%20appointment%20of%20Ashok%20Vaswani%20as%20the%20next%20MD%20and%20CEO%20of%20KMB.%20Ashok%20is%20a%20global%20banking%20leader%20with%20a%20proven%20track%20record%20of%20building%20and%20growing%20businesses%20at%20an%20international%20scale%20and%20has%20successfully%20steered%20organisations%20to%20greater%20heights.%20We%20are%20confident%20that%20Ashok%20will%20accelerate%20change%20and%20drive%20growth%20at%20Kotak.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUday%20Kotak%2C%20founder%20and%20director%2C%20KMB%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fudaykotak%2Fstatus%2F1715663361277296851%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%C2%A0%E2%80%9CI%20am%20delighted%20that%20the%20RBI%20has%20approved%20our%20recommendation%2C%20Ashok%20Vaswani%2C%20as%20the%20next%20CEO%20of%20Kotak%20Mahindra%20Bank.%20Ashok%20is%20a%20world%20class%20leader%20and%20banker%20with%20digital%20and%20customer%20focus.%20I%20am%20proud%20that%20we%20bring%20a%20%E2%80%98Global%20Indian%E2%80%99%20home%20to%20build%20Kotak%20and%20India%20of%20tomorrow.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbanking%2Fhigh-attrition-rate-at-kotak-mahindra-bank-fails-to-find-a-spot-in-annual-report%5C%22%3EThe%20Issue%20of%20High%20Attrition%20Rate%20at%20Kotak%20Mahindra%20Bank%20Fails%20to%20Find%20a%20Spot%20in%20Annual%20Report%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIgnoring%20internal%20talent%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETypically%2C%20successful%20organisations%20take%20pride%20in%20grooming%20CEOs%20from%20within.%20The%20board%E2%80%99s%20Nomination%20and%20Remuneration%20Committee%20is%20responsible%20for%20nurturing%20internal%20talent%20for%20leadership%20succession%2C%20especially%20for%20strategic%20posts%20such%20as%20the%20post%20of%20the%20CEO.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20Aditya%20Puri%20retired%20from%20HDFC%20Bank%2C%20Sashi%20Jagdishan%20(then%2056%20years%20of%20age)%2C%20a%20senior%20HDFC%20Bank%20executive%2C%20succeeded%20him.%20In%20ICICI%20Bank%2C%20after%20Chanda%20Kochhar%20was%20sacked%20by%20the%20board%2C%20Sandeep%20Bakshi%20(then%2058%20years)%2C%20a%20long-serving%20ICICI%20Bank%20senior%20executive%2C%20was%20appointed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20contrast%2C%20in%20the%20case%20of%20banks%20in%20which%20outside%20candidates%20replaced%20the%20CEOs%2C%20it%20was%20either%20because%20the%20banks%20were%20facing%20some%20serious%20issues%20and%20internal%20candidates%20were%20regarded%20as%20being%20part%20of%20the%20problem%2C%20or%20because%20the%20RBI%20lacked%20confidence%20in%20the%20internal%20candidates%20recommended%20by%20the%20board.%20Such%20were%20the%20cases%20in%20Axis%20Bank%2C%20when%20Amitabh%20Chaudhry%20(then%2055%20years)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Findia-business%2Faxis-bank-appoints-amitabh-chaudhry-as-md-and-ceo-to-take-charge-from-jan-1%2Farticleshow%2F65734385.cms%5C%22%3Etook%20charge%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20Shikha%20Sharma%3B%20in%20Yes%20Bank%2C%20when%20Ravneet%20Gill%20(then%2056%20years)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fmarkets%2Fstocks%2Fnews%2Fravneet-gill-to-replace-rana-kapoor-as-yes-bank-md-ceo%2Farticleshow%2F67671220.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Ereplaced%3C%2Fa%3E%20Rana%20Kapoor%3B%20and%20in%20RBL%20Bank%2C%20when%20R.%20Subramaniakumar%20(then%2063%20years)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businesstoday.in%2Fmagazine%2Fbanking%2Fstory%2Fcan-new-md-ceo-r-subramaniakumar-turn-around-rbl-banks-fortunes-341481-2022-07-14%5C%22%3Ereplaced%3C%2Fa%3E%20Vishwavir%20Ahuja.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20KMB%E2%80%99s%20case%2C%20the%20members%20of%20Uday%20Kotak%E2%80%99s%20leadership%20coterie%20were%20all%20employees%20who%20had%20been%20associated%20with%20the%20bank%2Fgroup%20for%20a%20long%20period.%20It%20was%2C%20therefore%2C%20highly%20unusual%20for%20the%20board%20of%20directors%20