environment%2C%20culture%20and%20senior%20executives.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENow%20Vaswani%2C%20with%20negligible%20experience%20in%20Indian%20banking%2C%20will%20be%20parachuted%20from%20a%20pleasant%20retirement%20from%20global%20commercial%20banking%20directly%20into%20the%20KMB%20CEO%20post.%20On%20landing%2C%20he%20is%20expected%20to%20do%20wonders%20in%20implementing%20a%20digital%20strategy%20in%20the%20Indian%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAn%20alternative%20explanation%20for%20the%20selection%20of%20Vaswani%20is%20that%20he%20was%20a%20last-minute%20selection%3B%20the%20banking%20regulator%2C%20the%20RBI%2C%20may%20have%20informed%20the%20KMB%20board%20that%20it%20would%20not%20approve%20an%20internal%20candidate%2C%20as%20it%20was%20uncomfortable%20with%20Uday%20Kotak%E2%80%99s%20continuance%20on%20the%20board%20as%20a%20non-executive%20director.%20This%20analyst%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhemindrahazari.com%2F2023%2F04%2F19%2Fafter-twenty-years-kotak-mahindra-bank-still-cant-manage-without-uday-kotak%2F%5C%22%3Eargued%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Uday%20Kotak%E2%80%99s%20retention%20on%20the%20board%20as%20a%20non-executive%20non-independent%20director%20would%20make%20him%20effectively%20the%20back-seat%20driver%20of%20the%20bank%2C%20without%20any%20of%20the%20associated%20responsibilities%20that%20come%20with%20such%20a%20position.%20It%20is%20poor%20corporate%20governance%20to%20allow%20a%20long-serving%20promoter%20CEO%20to%20continue%20on%20the%20board%20as%20a%20non-executive%20director%20after%20stepping%20down%20as%20the%20CEO.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIf%20Vaswani%E2%80%99s%20selection%20was%20made%20under%20such%20circumstances%2C%20on%20account%20of%20Uday%20Kotak%E2%80%99s%20continuance%20on%20the%20board%2C%20then%20again%20the%20Nomination%20and%20Remuneration%20Committee%20and%20the%20board%20have%20to%20be%20held%20accountable.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20last%20five%20years%2C%20KMB%E2%80%99s%20stock%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2F