ider.com%2F653859040487ff031cad7317%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20fried%20chicken%20from%20Popeyes%20is%20served%20in%20a%20tray%20lined%20with%20branded%20paper.%3Cp%3ENancy%20Luna%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20hard%20to%20get%20a%20complete%20bite%20because%20the%20breading%20fell%20off%20as%20soon%20as%20I%20picked%20up%20a%20large%20piece%20of%20chicken.%20It%20was%20greasy%2C%20but%20not%20as%20sticky%20and%20messy%20as%20KFC's%20chicken.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20ended%20up%20using%20a%20spork%20to%20eat%20some%20of%20the%20meat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20of%20sporks%2C%20they're%20cute%20and%20versatile.%20But%20I'd%20prefer%20to%20have%20forks%2C%20spoons%20and%20knives%20as%20my%20cutlery.%20Are%20sporks%20a%20fried%20chicken%20chain%20tradition%20because%20KFC%20also%20had%20sporks%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EKFC's%20fried%20chicken%20didn't%20live%20up%20to%20its%20finger-lickin'%20good%20reputation.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22KFC%20FRIED%20CHICKEN%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65385b70356802a56be2f1b7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKFC's%20fried%20chicken%20was%20super%20greasy.%3Cp%3ENancy%20Luna%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20ordered%20the%20mild%20fried%20chicken%20at%20Popeyes%20and%20compared%20it%20to%20KFC's%20original%20recipe%20chicken.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20expected%20to%20be%20dazzled%20by%20KFC's%20chicken.%20The%20breading%20on%20the%20skin%20was%20darker%20than%20Popeyes'%2C%20giving%20me%20the%20impression%20that%20I%20was%20going%20to%20get%20a%20very%20seasoned%20crunchy%20bite.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20chicken%20was%20juicy%20but%20also%20very%20greasy.%20In%20fact%2C%20I%20couldn't%20eat%20any%20more%20because%20my%20chicken%20kept%20slipping%20through%20my%20fingers%20as%20my%20hands%20were%20lathered%20in%20oil