%99%20for%20women%20and%20providing%20gas%20cylinders%20for%20Rs%20500.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20situation%20that%20has%20been%20created%20is%20nothing%20to%20worry%20about.%20This%20is%20their%20misconception.%20We%20will%20give%20more%20guarantees.%20We%20will%20announce%20another%205%20guarantees%20tomorrow.%20They%20can%20decide%20now%20where%20to%20raid%20next.%20This%20is%20the%20situation%20in%20a%20democracy%2C%20where%20a%20government%2C%20instead%20of%20winning%20the%20hearts%20of%20the%20people%2C%20instead%20uses%20its%20means%2C%20policies%20for%20the%20people%2C%20you%20are%20doing%20goondagardi%20(hooliganism).%20Without%20pressure%20from%20the%20top%2C%20neither%20the%20ED%20nor%20the%20CBI%20nor%20the%20Income%20Tax%20can%20come.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FWATCH%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23WATCH%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%20Jaipur%20%7C%20On%20ED%20raids%20on%20properties%20of%20Govind%20Singh%20Dotasra%20and%20ED%20summon%20to%20Vaibhav%20Gehlot%2C%20Rajasthan%20CM%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6The%20situation%20today%20is%20worrying.%20The%20question%20is%20not%20about%20someone%2C%20the%20question%20is%20not%20about%20my%20son.%20They%20have%20spread%20terror%20across%20the%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FAEDDdRINGo%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FAEDDdRINGo%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20ANI%20(%40ANI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FANI%2Fstatus%2F1717444368435732507%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EOctober%2026%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20these%20agencies%20keep%20their%20credibility%20intact%20then%20all%20states%20where%20there%20would%20be%20financial%20irregularities%20would%20say%20that%20let%20us%20hand%20over%20the%20probe%20to%20the%20CBI.%20But%20today%20the%20opposite%20is%20taking%20place.%20The%20situation%20is%20worrying.%20The%20question%20is%20not%20about%20my%20son.%20It%20is%20about%20terrorising%20the%20whole%20country.%C2%A0%20I%20have%20heard%20that%20ED%20officers%20have%20shifted%20their%20families%20to%20Chhattisgarh%20for%20a%20year%20now%20and%20are%20living%20there%20on%20rent%20because%20they%20have%20to%20conduct%20raids%20every%20day%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20is%20probing%20the%20Rs%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fed-cannot-be-a-law-unto-itself-supreme-court-says%5C%22%3E2%2C161-crore%20liquor%20scam%3C%2Fa%3E%20case%20in%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20in%20which%20senior%20government%20functionaries%20have%20been%20arrested%20and%20their%20bail%20pleas%20have%20been%20rejected%20by%20the%20Chhattisgarh%20high%20court%20recently.%20The%20incumbent%20government%20is%20also%20facing%20allegations%20of%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fvendetta-congress-ed-raid-chhattisgarh%5C%22%3Ecoal%20levy%20scam%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%20which%20two%20Congress%20MLAs%20and%20an%20IAS%20officer%20are%20named%20as%20accused.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20August%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20rapped%20the%20ED%20and%20said%20that%20it%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fed-cannot-be-a-law-unto-itself-supreme-court-says%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9Ccannot%20be%20a%20law%20unto%20itself%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewhile%20restraining%20the%20central%20probe%20agency%20and%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20government%20from%20proceeding%20with%20a%20fresh%20case%20against%20an%20accused%20in%20an%20alleged%20liquor%20scam%20in%20Chhattisgarh.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20press%20conference%2C%20Rajasthan%20Congress%20in-charge%20Sukhjinder%20Singh%20Randhawa%20said%20that%20it%20was%20%E2%80%9Cblack%20day%20for%20democracy%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20has%20never%20happened%20before%20during%20elections.%20A%20new%20trend%20has%20begun%20in%20Rajasthan%20and%20the%20Congress-ruled%20states%20that%20go%20to%20polls.%20I%20would%20like%20to%20ask%20the%20BJP%20government%20if%20they%20have%20anything%20else%20except%20IT%2C%20ED%20and%20CBI.%20Congress%20will%20not%20be%20scared.%20BJP%20should%20show%20the%20symbols%20of%20ED%2C%20CBI%20and%20IT%20along%20with%20its%20%E2%80%98Lotus%E2%80%99%20symbol.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20press%20conference%20in%20Delhi%2C%20Union%20minister%20Gajendra%20Singh%20Shekhawat%20said%20that%20the%20Gehlot%20government%20had%20crossed%20all%20milestones%20of%20corruption.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Ashok%20Gehlot%20government%20has%20crossed%20all%20the%20milestones%20of%20corruption%20and%20has%20set%20new%20benchmarks.%20A%20series%20of%20paper%20leaks%20took%20place%20in%20Rajasthan%20putting%20the%20future%20of%20lakhs%20of%20youth%20in%20darkness.%2070%20lakh%20youth%20of%20Rajasthan%20suffered%20due%20to%20continuous%2019%20paper%20leaks%E2%80%A6%20Most%20of%20them%20belonged%20to%20poor%20and%20Dalit%20families.%20They%20had%20hopes%20of%20a%20government%20job%20that%20would%20give%20their%20families%20dignity.%20They%20struggled%20to%20give%20an%20education%20to%20their%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6The%20main%20point%20here%20is%20that%20from%20the%201st%20till%20the%2019th%20paper%20leak%2C%20the%20people%20in%20government%20seemed%20to%20cover%20up%20the%20paper%20leaks%E2%80%A6%20CM%20Gehlot%20said%20that%20such%20incidents%20are%20normal%20and%20happen%20in%20other%20states%20too.%20Then%20he%20said%20that%20he%20would%20order%20an%20inquiry.%20Then%20he%20said%20that%20no%20government%20official%20was%20involved%20in%20it%20and%20gave%20a%20clean%20chit%20to%20them.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20to%20news%20agency%20ANI%2C%20Vaibhav%20Gehlot%20also%20said%20that%20he%20had%20received%20the%20summons%20from%20ED%3A%20%E2%80%9CAbout%20twelve-thirteen%20years%20ago%20similar%20allegations%20were%20made%20and%20we%20had%20responded%20to%20them.%20Now%20again%2C%20ED%20has%20come%20again.%20People%20of%20Rajasthan%20do%20understand%20why%20this%20is%20happening%20when%20model%20code%20of%20conduct%20is%20imposed%20in%20the%20state.%20ED%20raids%20have%20also%20been%20conducted%20on%20the%20state%20Congress%20chief%E2%80%99s%20premises.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOpposition%20hits%20out%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOpposition%20parties%20have%20lashed%20out%20at%20the%20BJP%20after%20the%20ED%20action%20in%20Rajasthan.%20AAP%20MLA%20Saurabh%20Bharadwaj%20said%20that%20the%20raids%20are%20not%20surprising%20anymore.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%2C%20Congress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20said%20that%20as%20soon%20as%20elections%20approach%2C%20%E2%80%9CED%2C%20CBI%2C%20IT%20etc.%20become%20the%20real%20%E2%80%98Panna%20Pramukh%E2%80%99%20of%20BJP.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22hi%5C%22%3E%E0%A4%9A%E0%A5%81%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%B5%20%E0%A4%86%E0%A4%A4%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%B9%E0%A5%80%20ED%2C%20CBI%2C%20IT%20%E0%A4%86%E0%A4%A6%E0%A4%BF%20%E0%A4%AD%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%9C%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%BE%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%85%E0%A4%B8%E0%A4%B2%E0%A5%80%20%E2%80%98%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%A8%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%BE%20%E0%A4%AA%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%AE%E0%A5%81%E0%A4%96%E2%80%99%20%E0%A4%AC%E0%A4%A8%20%E0%A4%9C%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%A4%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%B9%E0%A5%88%E0%A4%82%E0%A5%A4%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%9C%E0%A4%B8%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%A5%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%A8%20%E0%A4%AE%E0%A5%87%E0%A4%82%20%E0%A4%85%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%A8%E0%A5%80%20%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%B6%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%9A%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%A4%20%E0%A4%B9%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%B0%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%8B%20%E0%A4%A6%E0%A5%87%E0%A4%96%E0%A4%A4%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%B9%E0%A5%81%E0%A4%8F%20%E0%A4%AD%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%A4%E0%A5%80%E0%A4%AF%20%E0%A4%9C%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%BE%20