improbable-looking%20shots%2C%20the%20likes%20of%20which%20only%20he%20is%20capable%20off.%20While%20there%20were%20quite%20a%20few%20unorthodox%20and%20crazy%20shot%2C%20two%20shots%20against%20Bas%20De%20Leede%20stood%20out.%20In%20the%2047th%20over%2C%20Maxwell%20revere-hit%20the%20Netherlands%20bowler%20for%20two%20sixes.%20It%20was%20outrageous.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20Australian%20innings%20ended%2C%20former%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20captain%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Sunil%20Gavaskar%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F40594-sunil-manohar-gavaskar-playerprofile%5C%22%3ESunil%20Gavaskar%3C%2Fa%3E%20paid%20a%20rich%20tribute%20to%20Glenn%20Maxwell.%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20one%20(Reverse%20hit)%20has%20got%20to%20be%20one%20of%20the%20greatest%20cricketing%20shots.%20It's%20gone%20for%20six.%20It%20should%20be%20a%2012.%20The%20bowling%20after%20that%20got%20a%20bit%20rattled%20because%20they%20just%20didn't%20know%20where%20to%20bowl.%20It%20was%20an%20incredible%20effort.%20He%20had%20an%20average%20of%2012%2C%20to%20score%20the%20runs%20that%20he%20did%20and%20at%20the%20rate%20at%20which%20he%20did.%20It%20was%20amazing%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Gavaskar%20on%20Star%20Sports.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20took%2040%20balls%20to%20get%20off%20the%20mark.%20He%20has%20scored%20a%20hundred%20in%2040%20balls%2C%20amazing%2C%20amazing%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20Australia%20clinched%20a%20stunning%20309-run%20win%20against%20the%20Netherlands%20in%20the%2024th%20match%20of%20the%20ODI%20World%20Cup%202023%20at%20Arun%20Jaitley%20Stadium%20in%20Delhi%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20star%20allrounder%20Glenn%C2%A0Maxwell%C2%A0said%20that%20it%20was%20a%20bit%20weird%2C%20he%20had%20to%20calm%20himself%20down%20for%20the%20first%2020%20oddballs%20and%20rebuild.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20speaking%20at%20the%20pre-match%20press%20conference%2C%C2%A0Maxwell%C2%A0said%20that%20the%20circumstances%20and%20the%20timings%20of%20the%20wickets%20have%20changed%20the%20way%20he%20would%20have%20gone.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMaxwell%C2%A0added%20that%20he%20was%20just%20hitting%20the%20ball%20flat%20through%20the%20gap%20and%20picked%20the%20spots%20pretty%20clearly.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Aussie%20allrounder%20added%20that%20it%20was%20only%20the%20back%20end%20where%20I%20tried%20to%20just%20pump%20everything.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20bit%20weird%20that%20I%20had%20to%20calm%20myself%20down%20for%20the%20first%2020%20oddballs%20and%20rebuild.%20I%20think%20the%20circumstances%20of%2C%20I%20suppose%2C%20the%20timing%20of%20the%20wickets%20probably%20changed%20the%20way%20I%20would%20have%20gone%20about%20it%20if%20it%20was%20just%20me%20and%20Davey%20at%20the%20back%20end.%20I%20felt%20like%20I%20was%20just%20super%20selective.%20Even%20with%20the%20boundaries%20I%20was%20hitting%2C%20until%20I%20got%20to%20about%2050%20or%2060%2C%20I%20was%20literally%20hitting%20them%20flat%20through%20the%20gap%20or%20picking%20my%20spots%20pretty%20clearly%20where%20I%20wanted%20to%20go%20and%20it%20was%20only%20the%20back%20end%20where%20I%20tried%20to%20just%20pump%20everything%2C%26quot%3B%C2%A0Maxwell%C2%A0said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20talking%20about%20the%20inning%20against%20Netherlands%2C%C2%A0Maxwell%C2%A0said%20that%20he%20played%20a%20lot%20of%20games%20in%20India%20which%20helped%20him%20to%20score%20the%20fastest%20century%20at%20the%20ODI%20World%20Cup.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20added%20that%20he%20is%20not%20too%20worried%20about%20people%20saying%20that%20he%20hasn't%20made%20runs%20in%20ODI%20cricket%20because%20it%20doesn't%20really%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A0With%20ANI%20inputs%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698311340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Ftgrcktq8_glenn-maxwell_625x300_26_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fi-