hi%20said%20the%20hoarding%20has%20been%20put%20up%20by%20a%20party%20worker%20and%20is%20an%20expression%20of%20what%20he%20and%20other%20workers%20feel.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20often%20seen%20in%20politics%2C%20it%20is%20an%20expression%20of%20party%20workers'%20feelings%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Tripathi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EReacting%20sharply%2C%20Samajwadi%20Party%20state%20spokesperson%20Hasan%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BBoth%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20BJP%20are%20the%20same%20and%20the%20Samajwadis%20have%20been%20saying%20this%20for%20long.%20Any%20party%20can%20put%20up%20posters%20as%20per%20their%20sentiment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20which%20is%20fighting%20the%20battle%20of%20backwards%2C%20Dalits%20and%20minorities.%20No%20matter%20how%20many%20posters%20Congress%20puts%20up%2C%20the%20public%20wants%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20to%20be%20the%20PM.%20When%20an%20SP%20chief%20becomes%20a%20PM%2C%20an%20SP%20leader%20will%20become%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20UP.%20The%20vote%20share%20of%20Congress%20in%20UP%20is%20less%20than%20that%20of%20many%20regional%20parties%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Hasan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20poster%20put%20up%20by%20Hasan%20read%2C%20%26quot%3BHearty%20congratulations%20and%20best%20wishes%20on%20his%20birthday%20to%20the%20future%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20the%20country%2C%20respected%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20ji%2C%26quot%3B%20though%20Mr%20Yadav's%20official%20date%20of%20birth%20is%20July%201.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20last%20few%20days%2C%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20has%20publicly%20expressed%20his%20unhappiness%20with%20the%20Congress%20over%20the%20failure%20to%20arrive%20at%20a%20seat-sharing%20arrangement%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20had%20also%20referred%20to%20UPCC%20chief%20Ajay%20Rai%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bchirkut%26quot%3B%20(low-level)%20leader.%3Cbr%3E%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20N