it-surges-327-to-rs-1-756-cr-gross-npas-at-6-9-123102600506_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fresults%2Fpnb-q2-results-net-profit-surges-327-to-rs-1-756-cr-gross-npas-at-6-9-123102600506_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Maratha%20Quota%20Stir%3A%20Manoj%20Jarenge%20Patil%20Resumes%20Hunger%20Strike%20After%2040-Day%20Deadline%20to%20Govt%20Ends%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26132749%2FScreenshot-2023-10-26-at-1.27.15-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20A%20day%20after%20Maratha%20activist%20Manoj%20Jarenge-Patil%E2%80%99s%2040-day%20deadline%20to%20the%20Maharashtra%20government%2C%20the%20farmer%20activist%20resumed%20his%20indefinite%20hunger%20strike%20on%20Wednesday%20(October%2025)%20and%20said%20it%20will%20continue%20until%20all%20Marathas%20are%20given%20reservations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccusing%20the%20government%20of%20inaction%2C%20Patil%20rejected%20their%20plea%20to%20defer%20his%20protest%20any%20further%20after%20he%20called%20off%20the%20first%20phase%20of%20the%20protest%20on%20September%2014%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcities%2Fmumbai-news%2Fjarangepatil-resumes-hunger-strike-nixes-govt-s-request-to-postpone-it-101698262554126.html%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EMarathas%20from%20over%202%2C400%20villages%20have%20joined%20the%20agitation%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPatil%20and%20his%20supporters%20have%20been%20demanding%20that%20all%20Marathas%20be%20given%20Kunbi%20caste%20certificates%20to%20get%20the%20benefits%20of%20reservation%20in%20the%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20(OBC)%20category.%20Kunbi%2C%20a%20sub-caste%20of%20Marathas%2C%20are%20classified%20as%20OBCs.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERural%20development%20minister%20Girish%20Mahajan%20called%20Patil%20before%20he%20began%20his%20hunger%20strike%20at%2011%20am.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20want%20to%20give%20reservations%20that%20will%20stand%20up%20to%20legal%20scrutiny.%20The%20Justice%20Sandeep%20Shinde%20committee%20is%20working%20on%20the%20report.%20Chief%20minister%20Eknath%20Shinde%20has%20sworn%20on%20Chhatrapati%20Shivaji%20Maharaj%20in%20his%20Dussehra%20rally%20that%20he%20will%20give%20you%20reservation%20at%20any%20cost.%20He%20will%20personally%20speak%20to%20you%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mahajan%20was%20heard%20telling%20Patil%2C%20who%20made%20the%20conversation%20public%20by%20turning%20on%20his%20phone%20speaker.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fmaratha-quota-stir-bjps-plan-for-2024-lok-sabha-polls-under-threat-from-ongoing-protests%5C%22%3EMaratha%20Quota%20Stir%3A%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Plan%20For%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20Polls%20Under%20Threat%20From%20Ongoing%20Protests%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20asked%20for%2030%20days%2C%20we%20gave%20you%2041%2C%20but%20nothing%20was%20done%2C%E2%80%9D%20Patil%20told%20Mahajan.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20no%20way%20we%20will%20call%20off%20the%20protest%2C%20as%20our%20youths%20are%20suffering.%20The%20government%20had%20promised%20that%20it%20would%20withdraw%20the%20cases%20against%20protesters%20after%20the%20September%201%20lathi%20charge%20but%20nothing%20has%20been%20done.%20It%20looks%20like%20the%20government%20is%20playing%20tricks%20on%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20activist%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPatil%20added%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcities%2Fmumbai-news%2Fjarangepatil-resumes-hunger-strike-nixes-govt-s-request-to-postpone-it-101698262554126.html%5C%22%3E16%20Marathas%20had%20died%20by%20suicide%20in%20the%20last%20few%20days%3C%2Fa%3E%20but%20the%20government%20had%20done%20nothing%20to%20help%20their%20families.%20He%20also%20demanded%20that%20the%20farmers%20who%20suffered%20losses%20to%20their%20crops%20during%20the%20agitation%20be%20compensated%20by%20conducting%20a%20spot%20assessment.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20minister%20said%20that%20a%20legal%20process%20is%20required%20to%20withdraw%20police%20cases%20and%20that%20the%20concerned%20district%20collectors%20had%20been%20directed%20to%20help%20the%20families%20of%20those%20who%20died%20by%20suicide.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Maratha%20quota%20protests%20had%20begun%20on%20August%2029%20when%20Patil%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fexplainer-why-the-maratha-quota-agitation-has-put-successive-maharashtra-governments-in-a-bind%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ea%20Maratha%20activist%20from%20Jalna%2C%20sat%20on%20an%20indefinite%20hunger%20strike%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20reviving%20a%20three-decade%20old%20demand%20for%20Maratha%20reservations.%20In%20some%20places%2C%20the%20agitation%20turned%20violent%20with%20the%20police%20resorting%20to%20lathi-charge%20on%20the%20protesters%2C%20further%20worsening%20the%20situation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fmaratha-quota-stir-man-dies-by-suicide-leaves-note-demanding-reservation-for-community%5C%22%3EMaratha%20Quota%20Stir%3A%20Man%20Dies%20by%20Suicide%2C%20Leaves%20Note%20Demanding%20Reservation%20for%20Community%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Maharashtra%20government%20apologised%20for%20the%20lathi-charge%20and%20later%20announced%20that%20Kunbi%20caste%20certificates%20will%20be%20issued%20to%20those%20who%20possess%20revenue%20or%20education%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fthose-with-nizam-era-documents-recognising-them-as-kunbis-to-get-caste-certificates-cm-shindee%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edocuments%20