%20height%3D%5C%22664%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EAnish%20Malpani%20of%20%E2%80%98Without%E2%80%99%20says%20a%20few%20words%20after%20winning%20the%20Circular%20Design%20Challenge%20this%20year.%20Photo%3A%20Yasmeen%20Saadi%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98Without%E2%80%99%20uses%20Malpani%E2%80%99s%20patent%20pending%20technology%20to%20extract%20material%20from%20waste%20and%20turn%20it%20into%20sunglasses.%20The%20multi-layered%20plastic%20packaging%20found%20in%20waste%20like%20packets%20of%20chips%20and%20chocolate%20wrappers%20are%20%E2%80%9Cimpossible%20to%20recycle%E2%80%9D%20and%20almost%20always%20end%20up%20in%20landfills%20and%20oceans%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fashaya.in%2Fwithout%2F%5C%22%3Elabel%E2%80%99s%20website%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETalking%20with%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Malpani%20said%20he%20felt%20a%20call%20to%20do%20something%20more%20meaningful%20with%20his%20life%20while%20working%20in%20corporate%20finance%20in%20New%20York.%20He%20spent%20time%20in%20Guatemala%20and%20Nairobi%2C%20working%20with%20local%20entrepreneurs%2C%20before%20returning%20to%20India%20with%20a%20passion%20to%20work%20on%20the%20social%20and%20environmental%20causes%20of%20poverty.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMalpani%20was%20inspired%20to%20launch%20his%20startup%20after%20seeing%20the%20dangerous%20working%20conditions%20of%20waste%20pickers%20in%20his%20area%20and%20observing%20the%20environmental%20impacts%20of%20plastic%20waste.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20not%20just%20access%20to%20income%20or%20health%20care%20and%20education%2C%20but%20these%20are%20low-cost%20migrant%20workers%20with%20a%20life%20expectancy%20of%2018%20years%20of%20age.%20They%20work%20in%20waste%20without%20PPE%2C%20sometimes%20with%20the%20children%20on%20their%20backs%2C%E2%80%9D%20Malpani%20said.%20%E2%80%9CNot%20a%20fun%20situation%20at%20all.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20main%20missions%20of%20%E2%80%98Without%E2%80%99%20is%20to%20empower%20waste%20pickers.%20Malpani%20said%20the%20team%20currently%20consists%20of%2017%20members%2C%20including%20eight%20former%20waste%20pickers.%20For%20the%20waste%20pickers%20Malpani%20and%20his%20team%20work%20with%2C%20he%20said%20they%20try%20to%20help%20in%20multidimensional%20ways.%20So%20in%20addition%20to%20increasing%20income%2C%20he%20said%20the%20team%20helps%20waste%20pickers%20receive%20health%20care%2C%20provides%20scholarships%20to%20their%20children%20and%20helps%20make%20sure%20bank%20accounts%20are%20working.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%20waste%20picking%20should%20exist%20as%20an%20occupation%2C%20but%20you%20can%E2%80%99t%20displace%20%5Bwaste%20pickers%5D%20in%20negative%20ways.%20So%20how%20do%20you%20possibly%20displace%20them%20into%20their%20livelihoods%3F%E2%80%9D%20Malpani%20said.%20%E2%80%9CThat%20was%20the%20goal.%20And%20then%20the%20hypothesis%20became%20how%20do%20you%20fundamentally%20increase%20the%20value%20and%20use%20that%20to%20empower%20ways%20out%20of%20poverty.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20part%20of%20his%20design%2C%20the%20frames%20of%20Malpani%E2%80%99s%20glasses%20have%20a%20QR%20code%20inside%20which%20people%20can%20scan%20to%20see%20where%20the%20waste%20came%20from%20and%20the%20story%20of%20the%20waste%20picker.%20Malpani%20said%20it%20has%20been%20humbling%20to%20hear%20stories%20from%20waste%20pickers%20he%20works%20with%20and%20hopes%20to%20help%20break%20the%20cycle%20of%20the%20profession.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26124646%2FScreenshot-2023-10-26-at-12.46.26-PM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26124646%2FScreenshot-2023-10-26-at-12.46.26-PM.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26124646%2FScreenshot-2023-10-26-at-12.46.26-PM-300x167.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26124646%2FScreenshot-2023-10-26-at-12.46.26-PM-1024x571.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-681802%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22669%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EAnish%20Malpani%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Without%E2%80%99%20brand%20sported%20sunglasses%20made%20of%20%E2%80%9Cimpossible-to-recycle%E2%80%9D%20plastics.%20Stylists%20Daniel%20Franklin%20and%20Karishma%20Shahani-Khan%20styled%20the%20models%20for%20the%20Circular%20Design%20Challenge%20finale%20show.%20Photo%3A%20Yasmeen%20Saadi%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EGoing%20forward%2C%20Malpani%20said%20he%20aims%20to%20expand%20past%20sunglasses%20and%20use%20the%20versatility%20of%20the%20material%20to%20make%20more%20jewellery%20and%20accessories%20like%20mobile%20phone%20cases%20and%20watch%20straps.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLet%E2%80%99s%20be%20honest%2C%20sunglasses%20are%20not%20going%20to%20solve%20the%20waste%20problem%20or%20waste%20picker%20issue%20in%20India%20or%20the%20world%2C%E2%80%9D%20Malpani%20said.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20very%20strong%20proof%20of%20concept%3A%20that%20you%20can%20take%20this%20impossible-to-recycle%20plastic%20waste%2C%20convert%20it%20into%20high%20quality%20materials%20and%20products%20while%20empowering%20waste%20pickers%20to%20have%20a%20better%20life%2C%20because%20it%20is%20their%20livelihood.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20plans%20to%20widen%20the%20reach%20of%20%E2%80%98Without%E2%80%99%20by%20multiplying%20its%20recycling%20centres%20across%20India%20and%2C%20eventually%2C%20across%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20long%20run%2C%20we%20have%20to%20move%20volumes%20of%20material%20because%20that%E2%80%99s%20the%20