nd%20orders%20worth%20Rs%20202%20crore%20from%20the%20defence%20ministry%20earlier%20this%20year%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fzen-technologies-secures-rs-100-cr-order-from-mod-for-tank-training-system-123102600257_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Chinese%20'Research%20Ship'%20Docks%20at%20Sri%20Lankan%20Port%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F20111315%2F6136c82cc6d0df5736872b7c.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EChinese%20%E2%80%98research%20ship%E2%80%99%20%3Cem%3EShi%20Yan%206%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Earrived%20in%20Sri%20Lanka%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fnews%2Fasia%2Fsouth-asia%2Farticle%2F3239172%2Fchinese-research-ship-arrives-sri-lanka-year-after-similar-port-call-raised-concerns-india%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESouth%20China%20Morning%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%20In%20September%2C%20the%20Sri%20Lankan%20Ministry%20of%20Defence%20had%20given%20the%20ship%20permission%20to%20dock%20at%20Colombo.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fchinese-research-ship-given-permission-to-dock-at-sri-lankan-port-report%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Chinese%20%E2%80%9Cresearch%20ships%E2%80%9D%20are%20said%20to%20usually%20have%20dual%20purposes.%20While%20the%20primary%20aim%20is%20scientific%20exploration%2C%20what%20raises%20the%20hackles%20of%20other%20countries%20is%20the%20geopolitical%20purposes%20for%20which%20they%20are%20also%20deployed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CClearance%20was%20given%20for%20the%20vessel%20to%20come%20to%20Colombo%20for%20replenishment%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20Chinese%20foreign%20ministry%20spokesman%20told%20%3Cem%3ESouth%20China%20Morning%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBoth%20Indian%20and%20US%20officials%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fafter-india-us-raises-concern-with-sri-lanka-over-the-visit-of-chinese-research-vessel%5C%22%3Ereportedly%20expressed%20concerns%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20their%20counterparts%20in%20Colombo%20over%20the%20docking.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20China%2C%20Shiyan%206%20(Experiment%206)%20is%20out%20on%20an%20%E2%80%9Cexpeditionary%20voyage%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20eastern%20part%20of%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%2C%20after%20it%20had%20left%20Guangzhou%2C%20south%20China%E2%80%99s%20Guangdong%20Province.%20%E2%80%9COrganised%20by%20the%20South%20China%20Sea%20Institute%20of%20Oceanology%20(SCSIO)%20under%20the%20Chinese%20Academy%20of%20Sciences%2C%20the%20vessel%20is%20scheduled%20to%20operate%20at%20sea%20for%2080%20days%20with%2028%20scientific%20research%20projects%20from%2013%20research%20teams%20onboard%2C%20covering%20a%20range%20of%20more%20than%2012%2C000%20nautical%20miles%20(roughly%2022%2C200%20km)%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20report%20from%20China%E2%80%99s%20state-run%20news%20channel%20CGTN%20had%20said%20earlier%20this%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20concern%20over%20the%20visit%20of%20the%20Chinese%20vessel%20is%20due%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20it%20comes%20months%20after%20a%20Chinese%20warship%20was%20docked%20at%20the%20Colombo%20port%20for%20a%20few%20days.%20Earlier%2C%20another%20Chinese%20military%20ship%2C%20%3Cem%3EYuan%20Wang%205%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20had%20visited%20Sri%20Lanka%E2%80%99s%20Hambantota%20port%20in%20August%20last%20year%20even%20after%20India%20as%20well%20as%20the%20US%20had%20expressed%20their%20concerns.%20China%2C%20at%20that%20time%2C%20had%20said%20that%20it%20%E2%80%9Ccompletely%20unjustified%20for%20certain%20countries%20to%20cite%20the%20so-called%20%E2%80%98security%20concerns%E2%80%99%20to%20pressure%20Sri%20Lanka%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDespite%20Sri%20Lanka%E2%80%99s%20reassurances%2C%20India%20has%20conveyed%20to