n%20Gaza.%20There%20will%20be%20no%20electricity%2C%20no%20food%2C%20no%20water%2C%20no%20fuel.%20Everything%20will%20be%20closed.%20We%20are%20fighting%20human%20animals%20and%20we%20are%20acting%20accordingly.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20a%20rocket%20from%20Gaza%20is%20intercepted%20by%20the%20Iron%20Dome%20system%2C%20I%20can%20hear%20a%20loud%20explosion%20coming%20from%20the%20sky.%20The%20buildings%20shudder.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EI%20hear%20a%20sound%20and%20look%20at%20my%20friend.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20thunder%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20Only%20now%20do%20I%20notice%20that%20the%20sky%20is%20so%20cloudy%3B%20I%20have%20been%20too%20preoccupied%20with%20reading%20the%20news%20and%20my%20thoughts.%20The%20sounds%20of%20aircrafts%20and%20ambulances%2C%20and%20police%20sirens%20have%20also%20become%20startling.%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20was%20that%3F%E2%80%9D%20we%20ask%20each%20other%20frequently.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20narrow%20and%20long%20bomb%20shelter%20in%20the%20basement%20is%20full%20of%20residents%20from%20the%20floors%20above.%20There%20is%20a%20dog%20here%20too%2C%20who%20seems%20stressed%20out%20by%20the%20crowd%2C%20or%20maybe%20the%20war.%20It%20is%20recommended%20to%20be%20in%20the%20shelter%20for%2010%20minutes%20after%20the%20siren%20sounds.%20Someone%20has%20brought%20a%20plate%20of%20cookies%20to%20share.%20I%20took%20a%20cookie%20and%20now%20this%20dog%20is%20very%20interested%20in%20me.%20A%20friend%20texted%20and%20asked%20me%20if%20I%20am%20okay%20%E2%80%93%20she%20knew%20that%20there%20was%20a%20siren%20in%20my%20area%20because%20of%20an%20app%2C%20which%20notifies%20users%20of%20sirens%20in%20any%20of%20their%20selected%20areas%20in%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20woman%20on%20the%20other%20side%20of%20the%20shelter%20seems%20to%20be%20having%20a%20panic%20attack.%20I%20hear%20that%20PTSD%20is%20common%20within%20Israeli%20society.%20Many%20have%20traumatising%20experiences%20during%20their%20mandatory%20military%20service.%20Military%20service%20appears%20to%20be%20one%20of%20the%20core%20parts%20of%20being%20%E2%80%9CIsraeli%E2%80%9D%3B%20friends%20tell%20me%20that%20when%20strangers%20meet%20they%20often%20try%20to%20find%20mutual%20connections%20by%20referring%20to%20the%20time%20they%20served%20in%20the%20military.%20They%20say%20that%20a%20job%20applicant%20who%20did%20not%20serve%20could%20be%20perceived%20negatively%20by%20employers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20406px)%2085vw%2C%20406px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26084900%2FPTLP4329.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22406%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26084900%2FPTLP4329.jpg%20900w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26084900%2FPTLP4329-225x300.jpg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26084900%2FPTLP4329-768x1024.jpg%20768w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-681764%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22542%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20map%20of%20Hebron%20created%20by%20B%E2%80%99Tselem%20showing%20the%20architecture%20of%20Israeli%20apartheid.%20Photo%3A%20Aman%20Abhishek%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20death%20toll%20is%20still%20rising.%20Nobody%20that%20I%20know%20personally%20has%20been%20physically%20hurt%2C%20but%20almost%20all%20my%20Israeli%20friends%20know%20someone%20who%20died%20or%20is%20missing.%20It%20is%20a%20small%20country%3B%20everyone%20seems%20to%20know%20everyone.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMy%20friend%E2%80%99s%20mother%20is%20describing%20how%20yesterday%20she%20went%20to%20a%20funeral%20of%20someone%20who%20died%20in%20the%20Hamas%20attack.%20The%20siren%20sounded%20when%20she%20was%20driving%20back%20home%2C%20and%20she%20stopped%20her%20car%20in%20the%20m