0Terror%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20concluded%20with%20the%20Taliban%20regaining%20power%20in%20Afghanistan%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EWatch%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Watch%20%7C%20What%20It%E2%80%99s%20Like%20To%20Be%20a%20Palestinian%20in%20Israel%3A%20Prof%20Dalal%20Iriqat%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Fwatch-what-its-like-to-be-a-palestinian-in-israel-prof-dalal-iriqat%5C%22%3EWhat%20It%E2%80%99s%20Like%20To%20Be%20a%20Palestinian%20in%20Israel%3A%20Prof%20Dalal%20Iriqat%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EI%20receive%20a%20flood%20of%20messages%20in%20a%20group%20chat.%20A%20Palestinian%20human%20rights%20activist%2C%20Issa%20Amro%2C%20is%20missing.%20Issa%20is%20a%20prominent%20activist%20based%20in%20Hebron%2C%20West%20Bank.%20For%20many%20years%20he%20has%20fought%20against%20Israeli%20apartheid%20as%20well%20as%20human%20rights%20violations%20by%20Palestinian%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20group%20consists%20mainly%20of%20Jewish%20peace%20activists%2C%20many%20of%20whom%20I%20know%20and%20have%20become%20friends%20with.%20The%20messages%20are%20describing%20that%20the%20Israeli%20military%20took%20Issa%20to%20an%20unknown%20location%20and%20nobody%20has%20been%20able%20to%20reach%20him%20for%20hours.%20People%20are%20sending%20worried%20texts%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20should%20we%20do%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPhone%20numbers%20of%20military%20offices%20are%20shared%20so%20that%20activists%20could%20call%20and%20ask%20for%20Issa%E2%80%99s%20whereabouts.%20Someone%20calls%20a%20number%20and%20reports%20on%20the%20group%3A%20the%20military%20official%20said%20that%20they%20do%20not%20have%20time%20to%20entertain%20these%20requests%20during%20wartime.%20Of%20course%20dissent%20and%20human%20rights%20will%20be%20trampled%20using%20the%20pretext%20of%20war%20and%20a%20state%20of%20emergency.%20What%20else%20could%20one%20expect%3F%20This%20is%20what%20happened%20in%20the%20United%20States%20after%2