20system%20would%20soon%20hamper%20her%20movements%2C%20they%20decided%20to%20move%20back%20to%20India%20where%20help%20would%20be%20more%20easily%20available%20for%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20she%20taught%20at%20the%20MES%20Kishore%20Kendra%20in%20Malleswaram%20but%20after%20a%20few%20years%2C%20as%20the%20disease%20progressed%2C%20she%20started%20to%20use%20a%20wheelchair%20and%20soon%2C%20the%20school%20became%20a%20thing%20of%20the%20past.%20A%20friend%20suggested%20she%20create%20a%20play%20area%20within%20the%20house%20compound%2C%20or%20perhaps%20a%20library.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20idea%20soon%20metamorphosed%20into%20a%20summer%20camp%20for%20children.%20Located%20at%20the%20couple%E2%80%99s%20home%20in%20Malleswaram%2C%20which%20was%20thrown%20open%20to%20the%20children%2C%20it%20was%20a%20big%20hit.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGreatly%20inspired%20by%20Sudha%2C%20teachers%20here%20worked%20voluntarily.%20Many%20were%20known%20to%20her%2C%20some%20whose%20children%20had%20been%20tutored%20by%20her.%20Her%20wisdom%2C%20patient%20listening%2C%20counselling%2C%20and%20encouragement%20to%20the%20teachers%2C%20proved%20a%20big%20motivating%20factor%20for%20the%20flock%20that%20increased%20over%20the%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSudha%20has%20been%20an%20inspiration%20for%20the%20entire%20MS%20community.%20The%20consistent%20work%20she%20put%20into%20designing%20the%20summer%20workshop%20for%20kids%20through%20meticulous%20planning%2C%20networking%20and%20creativity%20is%20no%20less%20than%20a%20learning%20opportunity%20for%20any%20business%20school%20student.%20Her%20positive%20attitude%20and%20demeanour%20is%20infectious%20and%20you%20cannot%20say%20no%20to%20a%20request%20from%20Sudha%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%C2%A0A%20Kala%2C%20managing%20committee%20member%2C%20Multiple%20Sclerosis%20Society%20of%20India%20(MSSI)%20of%20the%20Karnataka%20Chapter.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20though%20the%20camps%20have%20been%20discontinued%2C%20th