k%20care%20of%20all%20details%2C%20giving%20us%20the%20lesson%20of%20what%20true%20leadership%20was.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETo%20Vijetha%2C%20who%20works%20as%20an%20HR%20in%20an%20MNC%2C%20Siddhi%20Creations%20and%20the%20camps%20were%20%E2%80%9Can%20important%20part%20of%20my%20childhood%2C%20in%20framing%20our%20minds%20and%20adding%20value.%E2%80%9D%20Harshith%2C%20another%20student%20of%20the%20camp%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20green%20surroundings%2C%20the%20teachers%20and%20Sudha%20ma%E2%80%99am%20with%20a%20happy%20face%20are%20unforgettable.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESudha%20echoes%20these%20feelings%20when%20she%20says%20that%20it%20was%20the%20children%E2%80%99s%20smile%20and%20happiness%20that%20was%20the%20best%20part%20of%20the%20summer%20camps.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20a%20sense%20of%20satisfaction%20and%20contentment%20in%20running%20the%20camps%2C%E2%80%9D%20smiles%20the%20octogenarian%20from%20her%20wheelchair.%C2%A0%20Her%20voice%20is%20now%20feeble%20but%20the%20spirit%20is%20as%20strong%20as%20ever.%20There%20is%20talk%20of%20reviving%20the%20camps%20among%20the%20teachers%20who%20are%20excited%20and%20ready.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAuthored%20by%20Jayalakshmi%20Menon.%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EAll%20picture%20credits%20go%20to%20Sudha%20Iyengar.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande.%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698072965000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FIMG-20230928-WA0004_11zon-1698072330.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D332837%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20brainchild%20of%20Sudha%20Iyengar%2C%20Siddhi%20Creations%20was%20a%20venture%20to%20keep%20young%20children%20engaged%20fruitfully%20and%20joyfully%20during%20summer%20vacations%20while%20also%20picking%20up%20on%20essential%20life%20skills.%20With%20managing%20her%20Multiple%20Sclerosis%20condition%2C%20Sudha's%20smile%