0his%20classes%2C%20which%20are%20from%207%20am%20to%202%20pm%2C%20with%20a%2015-minute%20break%20in%20between.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20lunch%20again%20at%20the%20mess%2C%20Rohan%20rests%20till%203%3A30pm.%20From%20then%20on%2C%20he%20starts%20studying%20in%20three-hour%20stretches.%20He%20takes%20a%20tea%20break%20at%206%3A30pm%2C%20followed%20by%20some%20revision%2C%20and%20then%20has%20his%20dinner%20at%208%3A30pm.%20From%209pm%20to%20midnight%2C%20he%20studies%20again%20before%20going%20to%20bed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOut%20of%2024%20hours%2C%20Rohan%2C%20who%20is%20preparing%20for%20the%20NEET-UG%20entrance%20to%20get%20into%20a%20medical%20college%2C%20spends%207%20hours%20in%20class%2C%207.5%20hours%20in%20self-study%2C%20and%20merely%205.5%20hours%20sleeping.%20The%20remaining%20four%20hours%20are%20spent%20travelling%2C%20bathing%20and%20eating.%20He%20hardly%20has%20any%20time%20for%20himself.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20routine%20followed%20by%20most%20students%20in%20Kota.%20They%20come%20to%20this%20town%20in%20Rajasthan%20for%20NEET%20and%20JEE%20coaching%2C%20an%20entrance%20exam%20to%20get%20into%20the%20top%20engineering%20colleges%20in%20India.%20Police%20officials%20of%20the%20city%20state%20that%20almost%2060%20percent%20students%20are%20from%20Bihar%20and%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20with%20the%20rest%20being%20from%20Rajasthan%2C%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Uttarakhand%20and%20Maharashtra.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20these%20parents%20go%20to%20great%20lengths%20to%20send%20their%20children%20here%2C%20which%20also%20lays%20heavily%20on%20the%20minds%20of%20these%2015-18-year-olds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20come%20from%20an%20agricultural%20background.%20I%20always%20wanted%20to%20be%20a%20doctor%2C%20but%20seeing%20the%20other%20students%20here%2C%20who%20are%20equally%20good%2C%20many%20even%20better%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20not%20sure%20if%20I%E2%80%99ll%20even%20crack%20the%20exam.%20My%20parents%20can%E2%80%99t%20afford%20a%20paid%20seat.%20I%20might%20give%20the%20exam%20next%20year%20again%20if%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20clear%20it%20this%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Rohan.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDoes%20he%20have%20any%20career%20plan%20if%20medicine%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20work%20out%3F%20No%2C%20he%20emphasises.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20reality%20is%20that%20only%20a%20few%20of%20the%20roughly%202%20lakh%20students%20who%20flock%20to%20Kota%20each%20year%20(figures%20as%20per%20Kota%20police%20officials)%2C%20would%20be%20able%20to%20get%20into%20these%20few%20top%20institutes.%20What%20happens%20to%20the%20rest%20of%20them%3F%20Do%20they%20have%20Plan%20Bs%3F%20Do%20our%20education%20systems%2C%20parents%2C%20teachers%20equip%20students%20to%20handle%20failure%20and%20teach%20them%20that%20there%20is%20a%20life%20beyond%20these%20courses%20and%20colleges.%20The%20answer%2C%20which%20today%E2%80%99s%20statistics%20show%2C%20is%20a%20big%20NO.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKota%20has%20seen%20a%20rising%20number%20of%20suicides%20in%20this%20year%20alone%20with%20more%20than%2025%20students%20having%20taken%20their%20lives.%20Student%20suicides%20have%20increased%20across%20the%20country%20too.%20The%20National%20Crime%20Records%20Bureau%20(NCRB)%20data%20states%20that%2013%2C089%20students%20died%20by%20suicide%20in%202021.%20This%20alarming%20increase%20in%20deaths%20by%20suicides%20has%20forced%20the%20administration%20in%20Kota%20and%20the%20Rajasthan%20government%20to%20take%20action.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20spoke%20to%20a%20few%20crusaders%20who%20are%20working%20towards%20identifying%20depression%20in%20students%20and%20telling%20them%20that%20life%20is%20much%20bigger%20than%20just%20one%20exam.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Have%20a%20Plan%20B%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%