ayog%20buys%20in%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20in%202021-22%20that%20the%20A.T.E%20CF%20team%20decided%20to%20approach%20Niti%20Aayog%20which%20quickly%20bought%20into%20the%20scheme.%20In%20June%202018%2C%20Niti%20Aayog%20had%20brought%20out%20a%20report%20on%20%E2%80%9CComposite%20Water%20Management%20Index%E2%80%9D%2C%20which%20mentions%20that%20India%20is%20undergoing%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F262905%2Fmaharashtra-girl-cycles-drought-prone-farmer-water-conservation-pranali-chikte%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eworst%20water%20crisis%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20its%20history%20and%20that%20nearly%20600%20million%20people%20are%20facing%20high%20to%20extreme%20water%20stress.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20further%20mentions%20that%20India%20is%20placed%20at%20120%3Csup%3Eth%3C%2Fsup%3E%20amongst%20122%20countries%20in%20the%20water%20quality%20index%2C%20with%20nearly%2070%25%20of%20water%20being%20contaminated.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20model%20presented%20by%20the%20foundation%20to%20the%20Niti%20Aayog%20could%20be%20scaled%20very%20quickly%20at%20a%20fraction%20of%20the%20cost%20to%20unleash%20water%20security%20in%20drought%20prone%20regions.%20It%20was%20community-led%20with%20farmers%20bearing%20a%20portion%20of%20the%20cost%20and%20aligns%20almost%20perfectly%20with%20the%20Amrit%20Sarovar%20mission%20launched%20by%20the%20Indian%20government%20in%20April%202022%20where%20the%20plan%20is%20to%20rejuvenate%20and%20develop%2075%20water%20bodies%20in%20each%20and%20every%20district%20of%20the%20country.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20traditional%20approach%20of%20building%20new%20water%20bodies%2C%20dams%20and%20canals%20is%20more%20expensive%2C%20ecologically%20and%20environmentally%20damaging%20and%20often%20leads%20to%20large%20scale%20displacement%20of%20the%20locals%20in%20the%20area.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20in%20the%20last%20two%20years%2C%20